\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 The ones that lived was Lewis, Emma, Esther, William, Walter, Frederick, Fanny and Florrie. Those were the ones that lived.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you know how old your father was when you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. He was seventy-nine when he died in 1929.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 He would have been about forty-two when you were born?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was he younger than your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I don't know. No, I don't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 He was a farm worker?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 He worked on the same farm for forty-five years?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was that the first farm job he ever had?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 For the farm work - yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Before he became a farm worker did he ever have another job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
He used to work at Lower Hayford, Malthouse. And he worked at the railway - Hook Norton Railway for a little while helping to lay their tracks for the railway at Hook Norton. And he used to walk from Hook Norton - from }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 Wychford}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551  to Hook Norton and he used to walk from }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 Wychford}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551  to Hayford - Lower Heyford when he worked there. Lodged at Heyford all the week and just walk home Saturday and back Sunday night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was that before he married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 After that he became a farm worker?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 He came - became a farm worker and was farm worker all his life. Same farm and the same farmer.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did he ever have a part time job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Only barbering. You see he used to do the village barbering.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What days of the week did he do that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 The barbering? He used to do that at night. There was no half days. No time off in the week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 He wouldn't have worked on Sunday?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, no, not on no account.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 So he did that in the evenings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Anything else in the way of part time or casual jobs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
No, I don't think so. The only thing that he used to do when he did - if it was a wet day as he couldn't work - he had to lose his time but he used to go in the barn just down below - the parish barn, and thrash his allotment corn out a
nd that - yes, yes, that used to - be his main - you know - job when it was a wet day then, like that. But as for anything else on the sideline - I never remembered him doing anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What use did he make of their corn?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 It used to be ground into meal for the feeding the pigs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 His own pigs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 He never sold any of it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
No. No. We were more or less self supporting in those days. And you could buy from one another, you know, neighbour. If you were short of anything that the n
eighbour had got excess you could always get it. There was no control like there is today - where you buy your milk or your butter or anything like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you remember your father ever being out of work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Not out of work - only when - losing the wet days - time for wet days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was that often quite a long stretch of time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
In the wintertime - yes. Sometimes he'd lose as much as three days in the week. If all the odd jobs was done up on the farm they'd be sent home and they never had any money for it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Hard times weren't they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Where did your father come from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Hook Norton - yes. And my mother was born at Hook Norton - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you know if she had a job before she married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. I don't know - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You never heard her say if she was in service or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 After she was married do you remember her doing any part time work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I never heard her say anything about doing - you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And you don't remember it yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 She didn't do any field work at any time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
No. There was very little field work was done with women in my young days. They didn't grow their potatoes and peas and that like they do nowadays. No. No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did anyone else besides you and your brothers and sisters live in the house - relatives or lodgers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. Not with us - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did your mother ever pay anybody to help in the house in any way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Not 'til she became - old - quite old. She -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was that after 1918?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, before then. In 19 - about 1910 she used to have a woman come to do her washing every Tuesday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did she woman do anything else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. Only come to do the - help out with the washing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 The cleaning and all that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 She used to do all that herself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did she ever pay anybody to mind you children at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No. No. They never seemed to go out anywhere. No. She never saw the sea you know, never }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 travelled}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551  a bit by train any farther than Hook Norton to Oxford I remember she came to Oxford once to 
have her eyes tested. That'd be about 1910. And that was the only time ever I heard her say that she }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 travelled}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
 by train. And she was nervous then }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 travelling}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551  by train - she got my other - older sister to go with her.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Before she employed this woman how did she manage with the washing - did she do it herself at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was any washing ever sent out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You mentioned you had a lovely dress and then it was put away in a box because you didn't want to go to the wedding with a t
wenty year old man?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you ever have any other new clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
I remember I - I begged of my mother to get me a new dress. A friend of mine had got a lovely new dress and I said to mother - I would like a dress like that. And she s
aid, oh well, we'll see what we can do. And she bought me a - in material and made me a new dress and we always called it the plum pudding dress. Because it was a white dress with a - a round patterns similar to plum puddings. We always called that a plum
 pudding dress. And another dress I remember - it was red twill with white braid. Three rows of white braid round the bottom and some round the cuffs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 She made that one too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. She done all our dressmaking - she made all the men's shirts - ever
ything. That's how she learned me how to do dressmaking and - I remember the first time that ever she got me on to doing any sewing. She said, look she said, I've got eight yards of material here - Oxford shirting. She said I'll give you that if you'll ma
k
e two shirts up for Bert - that was my hubby. And I said, well I don't know how to do it. Well, she says, look here's one of Fred's shirts - that was my brother, - she says, take that home, unpick it, press it out and bring it back. She said, and I'll sho
w you how to cut it out. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 She showed me how to cut the new material out, she showed me how to tack it all up together and then I made it on the machine. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 The very machine I've got in the kitchen now. That was the first bit of sewing ever I done. And now there isn't - I don't think there's anything for what I could do.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did she ever buy you a ready made dress?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, she bought that red twill. That was ready made. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Anything else that you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, I don't think so. Not ready made.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did she make all the underwear and things like that for the girls?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. They used to make - what they - we used to wear chemises. They was - just a sleeve in - they got - a mini-skirt - mini-dress now.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did she do the mending?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Always.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did your father do anything in the way of sewing or tailoring or mending anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did your mother ever buy second hand clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When she did buy a dress like the red twill where was it bought?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 From a man who used to travel round door-to-door. He used... 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was that your uncle?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
No. Not - another man that lived at Rova Head. He used to come round with a pony and trap every Wednesday morning. And he used to bring different things - }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 children\rquote s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551  clothes as well. That's where she bought my red dress from.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Were you able to try it on then before you bought it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 It was left and then if it didn't fit I could - it could go back the next week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You bought some boots for five and eleven I think you said?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 For your brother, at Chipping Norton?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did your own boots come from the same shop?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was girls and boys?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you ever have second hand shoes or boots?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. Never.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you have hand-me-downs from the older ones?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. Because they were old - much older than I was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 If you wanted new shoes they were always new?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 It was always new.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When they needed repairing what happened?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 There was a blind shoemaker in the village. He used to mend the shoes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Nobody else ever did it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did your father help your mother with anything in the house such as cleaning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you ever remember him doing any cooking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 He always used to prepare the Sunday vegetable - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Anything else on a Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. He used to - usually got ready went to prayer meeting down at the chapel Sunday morning.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Would that be after he'd done the vegetables?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. He had a set - a very set time to do everything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 He was that sort of person was he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
Yes. He'd get up at six o'clock and he was quite a routine of his life all through. His meals was always at one set time and he'd never have any more than two slices of bread and butter for b
reakfast. I never remembered my mother frying for breakfast for my father. Just the bread and butter. Yes. He wouldn't - he wouldn't have any more than the two slices bread and butter.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 He had something to drink with it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 He used to have a cup of tea in the mornings and then he used to have a glass of beer - home brewed beer - in - when he fancied one.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you ever remember him washing up the dishes or lending a hand?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did he light or make the fires?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. Dad never seemed to 
trouble to - to think about helping the housewife. I never remembered my father doing anything in the house. Except just the vegetable on the Sunday morning.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Would he repair furniture?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 He would repair it - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 He did repairs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And any painting or decorating - did he ever do that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Mother used to do that. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you remember him making any improvement to the house at all?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Of course he had such long hours didn't he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes. And we'd got such a lot in the gardening you see. Used to do it all single handed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you ever remember him doing anything in the way of looking after you children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 He never dressed you or put you to bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did he tell stories and read to you and that sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did he ever take you out without your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Not my father - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 He didn't go for a walk with you or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did your mother ever go out and leave him in charge of the children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You had to take puddings to the baker didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 How often was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Oh - most every week. Once a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 On a regular day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Would the baker bake for the village people everyday of the week or just on a set day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 He'd bake anything that was took to him in the way of puddings, pies, pastry or joints or anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did your mother used it for joints as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Only the - special occasions.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Not a regular thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, not a regular thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Can you remember what it cost to have the puddings baked?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Penny. Yes. Yes, whatever the size it was a penny.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 If you took more than one would it still be a penny?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 It would be a penny, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You also had to go to the carriers on Thursday and order cheese?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Can you remember any other little jobs you had to do for your mother and father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Well I always used to have to fetch the - the milk and the butter. I walked half a mile to fetch a pint of milk - that was skimmed milk.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 As a regular thing was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
Yes. When certain farmer's cows had gone dry as they call it we had to have our milk from another farm and perhaps that was a half mile away. I used to fetch that after I'd done school at night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 As a general rule did the farmers bring the milk round themselves?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No, you had to fetch the milk.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you fetch that as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Always fetched the milk - that was a regular thing every night. - after school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you have any other things to do - were there regular jobs in the house you had to do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Saturday mornings.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Is that when you did your door knockers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 That was when I done my door knobs. Chopped the wood, cleaned the shoes. We all had our Sunday
 pair of shoes and that days. Even myself did. But they were boots.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Because of you being rough on your shoes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did the other sisters have Sunday shoes then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Well, my oldest sisters - they were married you see - when I was wel
l, going to school. And the - the next sister to me she died when she was sixteen. So I don't - don't know much about her. I remember when she died. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you go to the funeral?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. And she was along the garden the night before she died and 
picked some blackcurrants. Bought them along and she said she didn't want them - would I like them and I had them and that was the last time that she spoke to me. She went in and died the next morning before I was up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you wear black clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Even the children had to wear black at that time of day. And you wore black for twelve months.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you have any crepe or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. They would always - worn.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Where was that worn?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Oh, round your hat. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you wear those black clothes every day or just on Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 We had a - black dress for weekday and one for Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was it just the family at the funeral or did other people go too?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Sometimes other people'd come if you was very near friends - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 On that particular occasion do you remember who else went?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 It'd be just - just her friends you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 From your own family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 The village - the village. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 After you left school you went straight into service didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 So those jobs you used to do like the milk and all those little jobs - did you stop doing them then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I'd got to - yes. Yes. Mother had to do them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 She must have missed your help?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Can you ever remember doing anything to help the older children when they were at home - you had brothers at home still didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you remember doing little jobs for them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I used to have to do their errands, you know, fetch their tobacco and - yes, yes. They used to ask me to do that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 By the time you were at school there wasn't a sister at home then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 They were all in service?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did they come home on occasions?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. When they had their day off - home to mum. One day a month.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you do anything for them then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You didn't do errands for them or wait on them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you remember the older ones doing anything for you - making things for you or taking you out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You said nine-thirty was bedtime?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What age were you when that started to be your bedtime?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
Well - I used to have to go to bed at half past seven 'til I was leaving school. Yes. We - my sister and I up 'til the time she died - we used to - lay a bed 
and talk and my father'd got the clock hung up in there and when we heard him coming upstairs and wind the clock up we knew we'd got to stop talking and go to sleep.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What time would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Oh, half past nine - never no later than that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 He'd go up then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Very regular for bedtime.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did your mother ever put you to bed and did she supervise your bedtime?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When I was small she always used to put me up to bed, tick me in and kiss me goodnight after I'd said my prayers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 She used to hear you say your prayers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Always heard me say my prayers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Then you were in the bed with Fanny?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What age were you when you started seeing yourself to bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I should say I was about ten or eleven.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Would she still come up then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 She'd come up and see as we was all right. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You shared the bed with Fanny - was there anyone else in the room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Just the two of you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 How did the other members of the family sleep?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 We
ll - three - three brothers home for a little while I remember when I went to school. Then one got married and the other went to Oxford and that left only my brother Fred. He was six years older than I was. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And he was the only one at home then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did he have a room on his own or did he share with anyone?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 He had a room on his own.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And what about your mother and father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 They had their - they had one room and the boys always used to have the other room and Fanny and I 
had the third room. And after Fanny died if we had any visitors I used to go across the way to a friend of mine and sleep with her. And when they had visitors she used to come across to me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 She was a farmers daughter?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You mentioned having your hair washed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 On Friday nights?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Every Friday night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When did you bath?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Every Saturday - yes. In a washing bath. Galvanised washing bath.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 One of those round ones?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Oval ones - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Whereabouts was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, we used to have it in the - in the kitchen. Yes. By the fire as a rule in the winter time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When did you have clean clothes on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 After the bath. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And you had to keep those then for how long?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Clean clothes? Well, we used -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Up 'til the next week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Where did the family eat their meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 In the kitchen. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Were there any occasions when they ate in another room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. We always had Sunday tea in the sitting room. Always.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was that the best room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes. That was a panelled room. All lovely panelled.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you ever go into it at other times in the week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Oh, not very often
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 It was kept special?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 It was generally kept special.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Where did your mother cook?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 In the kitchen. On the -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 The same room that you ate in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What did she cook on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Kitchen range - that she bought herself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 She had it installed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. And then when the house furniture and that was sold the land agen
t allowed her half price on the stove. He allowed her thirty shillings off her rent - last rent I paid for 'em.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did it have a little oven at the side?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. It had a - quite a - quite a nice big oven. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You said your father had two slices of bread at breakfast time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did he eat with the rest of you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You all had breakfast together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 That must have been }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 quite early}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551  - or did he come back for breakfast?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. But that was about half 
past six to seven. Yes. We was always had to get up early in the morning. Ready to get up early because we had to go to bed so early.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You didn't lose much of the daylight then did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What did you have for your breakfast when you were a schoolgirl?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Oh, generally bread and butter.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And when you had to share an egg with your sister that you mentioned to me... ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What meal would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Tea time. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you ever have eggs at breakfast?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Anything ever cooked?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Just the bread?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, bread and butter.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And to drink?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, tea.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 That milk you used to fetch - was that ever drunk as a glass of milk?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Never. Never.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 It was used up in other things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, used up in cooking and in tea and that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was the mid-day meal your main meal of the day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What time would that be?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Half past twelve.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you come home for that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And who else had the mid-day meal with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
Well, most my school days it was just my mother, father and myself. 'Cos with my brother he was at work too far away to get home to dinner. He used to have his meal at night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Your father always came home for dinner?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Can you tell me a typical mid-day meal your mother would cook?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Oh a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 piece}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
 - bit of boiled bacon and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 From your own pig?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. And vegetables - had the vegetables in the garden. Self supporting they were with the vegetables.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did she never need to buy vegetables?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
Oh for a - for a pudding roly-poly jam pudding or currant pudding or whatever - and we always used to have our pudding first in that time of day. Yes. I asked my mother years after I said to my m
other I said they don't have their puddings first when you - go to service. Said why do you have your pudding first - why did you have your pudding first. She said - well, the pudding used to fill you more, she said, that's why we gave you the pudding fir
st. You didn't want so much meat.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 So even if it was a real sweet pudding it was first?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Always.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was there always a pudding - at every mid-day meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Most always - yes. Either steamed or done at the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 bake house}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did she ever do a tart or pie?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. She used to make a lot of pudding and tarts and pies.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 On a Sunday did you have anything different from usual?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. We always had it - beef steak and kidney pudding on the Sunday. Always the same. Year after year. Year af
ter year. And do you know I can never make a pudding like my mother made. Now and - no matter how I try now. I think it's the difference in the quality of the meat. Yes. Yes, lovely thick gravy.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did she do a special kind of pudding on those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 We didn't have a sweet on Sundays. No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you have vegetables and potatoes with the pudding?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Can you think of other things - did she sometimes cook liver for you?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 On a weekday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What other kind of meat did she get?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
She always bought a - a small joint of meat for Sunday. That was the only time we had butchers meat. That was about a shilling or one and... 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 The beef steak and kidney pudding that was on a Sunday too was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And the joint?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Well, she didn't have a joint.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I thought you said she always bought a small joint of meat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Well, it was a - a - beef steak - she'd buy the beef steak and she'd put that in a pudding - make a pudding. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Were there some days when you had no meat at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
We could always have bacon. We'd always got bacon. Yes. And I always got something to spread on your bread. Either home cured lard or butter.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What did you have for tea - did you have a tea all together in the afternoon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Five o'clock, yes, yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What did you have then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Bread and butter and cake. Jam. Home made jam.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was it always cake?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, because she'd make a lot of cake.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 She must have been a very good manager?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Oh yes. But things were so cheap at that time of day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did she make the cakes herself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
Yes. Make them herself. Now and again she used to order half a quarter of lard cakes. That was on the Friday, I used to order them as I went to school and collect 'em when I come back.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 That wasn't just for your uncles visit then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. That was for the special - special treat for Sunday now and - just now and again.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you have a different tea on Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you have supper before you went to bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 So five o'clock was the last food of the day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Not a cup of cocoa or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. Nothing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Can you remember if you had anything different at breakfast on Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was the food different in any way on Saturdays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Your father always came home didn't he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did your father or mother ever make bread?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 My mother used to make a loaf now and again. When father used to have one allotment wheat and t
he other barley and my brother used to plant his allotment potatoes. The wheat that was grown on the allotment my father used to have that threshed out and sent to the millers and mother used to make bread with that. Cakes. That used to help her a lot.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 How much weight was it - do you have any idea?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Oh, about a hundredweight. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you remember her getting bread from the baker as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 How much of the bread do you think she baked herself? Was it about half or less?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Well, she - probably make four loaves - in the week and buy four or five.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 So it was roughly half?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Regular throughout the year?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes. If she had - when they had the allotment planted wheat.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Only at those times?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 That's right - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 It would have been a third of the time wouldn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did she make her own jam?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 All of it or did she buy some?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, all of it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did she ever bottle fruit or vegetables?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. Was never heard of at that time of - my }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 school day}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551  - never heard of - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you remember her making pickles?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Used to make all her pickles.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 What}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551  types?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Pickled shallots and onions and she used to make a marrow pickle - yes
, marrow pickle and marrow jam. She contrived to do a marrow jam and pickle at the same time because it was a ripe marrow that was used you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Anything else in the way of pickles - cabbage or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Pickled cabbage - yes, the red pickled cabbage. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You told me about how your father brewed the beer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And the rhubarb wine and the cider?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Were there any other wines they made?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Mother used to make a drop of sloe wine. And elderberry wine.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 So they both made wine?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 She used to make these medicines out of egg and sugar and vinegar?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 She did a lot of }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 remedies}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551  didn't she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you remember any other ones?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 She used to get the marshmallow out of the garden and pound the leaves down and then boil them in lard and that was used for ointment.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 For what type of things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Anything. Cuts or bruises or anything like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Where do you think she got those recipes from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I think they was from her own parents you know. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did they grow fruit as well as vegetables?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Wonderful lot of fruit. Yes. Blackcurrants, redcurrants, }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 white currants}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 , gooseberries.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Apples?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Apples. No pears. We'd got four apple trees and I s
hould think dozens of gooseberry trees and currant trees. It were quite a business picking the fruit. I had that to do after I come home from school each night in the fruit season. And she used to do it all into jam. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You mean the currants weren't put in a tart or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, the - the jam - the - she used to make a blackcurrant and gooseberry pie. And rhubarb pies she used to make. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you ever remember her buying fruit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Never. Never. Never.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you remember her buying any tinned fruit or vegetables at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
No. Wasn't - wasn't on sale. No. If she sent me to the shop to fetch a glass of syrup - golden syrup - if I bought a tin of golden syrup I always had to take it back. She wouldn't have a thing out of a tin.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Why was that do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Well she used to think it wasn't good.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Sort of contaminated?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, she used to think it was a danger poisoning I suppose. They used to sell }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 the treacle}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551  in - half pint tumblers. They were thick - fluted so far around. She got dozens of those and - when we packed up housekeeping.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What about dried vegetables or fruit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Not even sultanas or currants?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Wonderfully self sufficient weren't they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, they were.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you remember her buying any tinned meat or fish?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You don't remember seeing it around?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. Never.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 A lot of people in those days used to get things from poaching or somebody would give them something poached - did your father
 do anything like this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Never.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You don't remember having anything in that way at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you think your father would have been against that sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 He wouldn't have approved?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you ever remember your mother having a bit less so that the others could have more?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
Sometimes - yes, yes. And sometimes if it was - she thought the bakers bill was a bit - was going to be a bit higher she'd buy a packet of Quaker Oats and make Quaker Oats and we'd have them to ease the situation with the bread.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Instead of bread you mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And that would be at breakfast?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did your father have more to eat - bigger helpings than the rest of you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 He had the same?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You weren't allowed to talk during meals were you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was that on no occasion ever?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, we never used to be allowed to speak at table - anytime. Unless we was spoke to. We never was allowed to speak at table.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Suppose you wanted some salt on your food -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 It would be on the table.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Could you ask for it to be passed to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You could speak for that sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes, but not to enter in any conversation at the table.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did your mother and father speak between themselves at meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Not very - not very often. Meals was almost a silent affair.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When your mother cooked the food could you choose what you wanted to eat or did you have to eat everything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, you could choose. If there was anything you wouldn't - didn't like we could just say and mother'd remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And she didn't mind?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 If you wanted something would she want you to finish it all up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 She would expect you to finish it - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And if you didn't would anything be said?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No, because we'd got chickens and that - it used to go out for the chickens.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You had chickens as well as pigs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was there anything else besides the chickens and pigs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 That was enough to keep you busy I should think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I wondered if you had any goats?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Could you ask for a second helping if you wanted some more?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Were you expected to hold your knife and fork in a certain way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And was she particular about how you sat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 We always used to have to sit upright at the table.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Suppose you put your elbows on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Oh, we wouldn't think of that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 She wouldn't approve?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did she ever have occasion to use that little cane that she used to keep?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 You felt}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551  it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 For what sort of things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Sometimes we'd have a joke before we went into the room to - you know - to meals and one'd look at the 
other, my brother d perhaps look at me and I'd start laughing and she - she'd fetch the cane out and rap me across the knuckles.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 But on the whole I think you said a look from her was enough?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. It was - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 If you wanted to bring a toy to the table when you were very little - could you have brought it to the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Not at meal time. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When could you leave the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When they'd all finished you'd say please may I leave the table - after grace was said. Grace was alw
ays said before and after meals. My father always said the grace.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was that at all the meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. All meals - every day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you all have the same places at the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 They never varied?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 How was the meal served? You say your mother and your father each had a little left to them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When I went to school. When my grandfather died he left my father two hundred pound.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And that was while you were at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Two hundred pound?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 That was a lot then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Oh, it was a wonderful lot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What did he do with it when he got it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 He kept it at home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 In the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, he bought some new furniture and he bought some new clothes for - fo
r us children and mother had a new dress and the remainder he kept. That was in gold sovereigns and he used to put it in a little velvet bags and put it in at bottom of the clock that hung up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was it a secret that it was there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I didn't know whe
re it was - even mother didn't know where it was. She was wondering what - where he'd put it - she couldn't find it anywhere and one night the bottom of the clock fell out - the weight broke from the cord and down came his bag of gold. And she found it th
e
n. But he moved it and he put it in his tip silk hat that he used for funerals. He always used to keep that and an ounce of tobacco that he had from the Jubilee celebration I should think it would be. Queen Victoria's Jubilee. They all had - the men had o
unce of tobacco in our village and he was a non-smoker, he used to think that keeping that ounce of tobacco in his chest with his clothes that kept the months away.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you think it did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, I think it did. He had that idea.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did he used any of the rest of the money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
Well, he had to use it - he was ill with rheumatic fever and he had seventeen weeks home. And there was no medical - benefit - only what we had from the parish. That was one loaf and a half-a-crown a week. And he used quite 
a lot of his money to keep going at that time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Your mothers money - when was that left to her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I was about twelve years old and - when she had that left. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 
And that was just over hundred pounds that. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 She really wanted to buy a house at Hook Norton. And she was just a little bit too late and so she just kept it and had little bit extras.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You mean she spent it on small things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Small things. They never banked any - neither of them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did she hide it too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Well, she used to keep
 it in the - she used to keep it in a bag hung on the top of her bedstead. It was a funny thing. She didn't hide it really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I suppose nobody would ever think... ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, never think - nobody ever think as there was going to be any robbery or burgla
ry at that time of day. And if there was one murder that was a - nine days wonder.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You didn't see the policemen round much then when you were a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was there one in your village?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, there was one in - next village.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 How did he treat the people at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Very good. There wasn't much - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What was your mother's fathers people - what was their job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Wheelwright and carpenters.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 They had their own little business?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And your fathers people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Just farm labourers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 They were farm labourers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 How were they able to save that amount of money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 To have it? My grandfather had a bit left him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What was the money from there do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I wouldn't know. But I know -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 They were also farm labourers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 The family were farm labourers for a long way back?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, but - from - I don't know - going back three or four generations I don't know whether - how they would come with that 
money. But I know there was - but my father had more than my mother did, from her side. Although my mother's parents to my idea was better off because they was wheelwright and carpenters for the village.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 That was in Hook Norton?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Undertakers and all they were at that time of day. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Making coffins I suppose?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 To get back to meals again - did your mother serve you in a particular order?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Usually father had his first then the children as they sat round the table. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When you were a little child can you remember were you fed separately before you could feed yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Don't remember.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You always remember eating with the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You don't remember a high chair or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was your mother easy to talk to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
Yes, but - you could discuss - discuss anything with her and ask her anything and she'd tell you, but - I think on the whole she was - what you may say - a most placid sort of person. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 If you were worried about something did you keep it to yourself or did you tell her.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I should go and ask her advice and she would tell me and she'd - she consoled me if she thought I needed consolation and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 She was that sort of mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 She was the sort of person who could show affection?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was your father an easy person to talk to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you feel as close to him as to your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, closer to my mother - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was he affectionate?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes. To all the family yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 How did your mother and father expect you to behave towards them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Well they expected you know - respect, to the highest degree and they way you spoke you know. I remember once my mother - I
 was down the garden and my mother called me. She said 'Florrie.' And I well remember I said - what? And she kept calling Florrie 'til I realised I had to say yes mother. But I had the belt when I got back for that. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Can you remember anything else because it's very interesting how times have changed in bringing up children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
Yes, it is. They'd never think about going out at night to leave you. I never remember my mother going out at - not at night with - to leave us children. Never.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did your father go out sometimes at night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. Only to chapel - if there was any chapel he'd go down there - that hall.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you remember your parents bringing you up to behave towards your brothers and sisters in certain ways?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, because they were so much older than I was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you and your sister Fanny quarrel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What did your parents say then - do you remember?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Used to give the one they thought was to blame a hiding.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 If another child hit you what would your mother say you should do about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Hit 'em back. Yes. She'd never interfere.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 But she told you to hit back if you were hit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What kind of people do you think your parents hoped you'd grow up to be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Well they - I suppose they would expect me to be a - honest, respectable, hard - working person. Which I always have been.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 They brought you up like this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 They always brought me up respectable and to be respected. And I must say that that's what I've - my lifetimes con
sisted of. I've always been respected and - had a very good life - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 The things they brought you up to think important in life - you mentioned your father said about telling about the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 truth}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And honesty.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Anything else you can remember they felt was important in life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
Well, to always respect other people and especially my elders - elderly people and to do whatever kindness I could for anybody - in the way of opening a gate or helping anybody over the road or anything. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What did your parents think about swearing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
Swearing was never allowed in the house. I never heard - remember anybody swearing until my oldest boy was on holiday and I suppose he'd been out with the other children in play and he 
said oh, damn it. I remember mother picking him up - he was about four - she picked him up and she sat him on the cupboard by the side of the fireplace so - so heavy. She didn't half give him a look. She told him, you know, about swearing. She blamed me f
or that but I - it wasn't me because I - I never thought about swearing because I'd been always brought up - you know - in a respectable way and - I never used bad language. I knew it was from children outside.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When you were a little girl you don't remember other children using bad language?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Not very often, no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was there a change to you think in people using bad language as time went on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I think so. I think after the first world war I think it's more so. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When grown ups were talking were you allowed to join in the conversation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What did you have to do if they were talking and you were there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Just sit and be quiet.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When you were punished - you say your father punished the boys and your mother punished the girls? Was that always the rule?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes. Always the rule - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You never remember your father punishing you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Never, never.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 There was the incident of getting the belt because you shouted out what?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Can you remember any other time when you were punished for anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No, not - not special - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did it happen very often?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was there any other kind of punishment that they gave you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 She put me to }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 Bed early}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551  - yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you remember a particular time when she did that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, I really don't remember what it was for.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 But you know she did that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. I remember having to go to bed early a time or two.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Would that mean you'd miss your tea?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You had your tea?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you remember how you felt that day after she gave you the belt?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I felt very bitter at the time but - I don't now. I think what a good upbringing I had. I don't regret a thing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Would you say that the ideas you had in life - did you get them more from your mother or more from your father or both about the same?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Both the same - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When you had a birthday would it be different from any other day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. I would have a packet of sweets perhaps. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When would they be given to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 In the morning the birthday - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Would there be anything special to eat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you ever have any other presents besides the sweets?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Well sometimes my sisters give me something.
 Always remember my brother gave me a doll and that was a yard long. It was a wax doll. That was always kept in the box and just fetched out very, very rare occasions. See, if I had a birthday I could have my doll out to play with and then it had to go ba
c
k in the box. You can tell how well I kept it - I had that when my brother went to Oxford Co-op to work and I should say I was about eight years old then and I got that doll when I was married and my oldest boy he used to play with it. He broke it however
.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you ever have any little friends in to tea or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I used to have my one girl friend across the way. Just now and again.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Would that be on birthdays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 If she invited me to her birthday party mother felt that she had
 to return the invitation. That was the only time that ever I had anyone to tea.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did your mother not like having people in to tea?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Wasn't a - wasn't a thing that was thought about really. No, they didn't entertain much. I suppose it was because they was so - poor.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Well, there was just enough to go round for the family wasn't there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Your friends people were farming - were they a bit better off?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. They were a bit better off than we were.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 On Christmas Day do you remember doing anything with your mother and father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, I remember my mother always used to put orange and apple in our shoes - in our boots Christmas morning.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No stocking you mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. We didn't have a stocking - didn't have our stock
ings up - not very often. They went - orange and apple went in the boot. But as we got older I well remember - I should think I was about ten or twelve - and mother thought we were too old, you know, to have our things give us - she used to parcel them up
.
 My brother and my sister and me there - we had a little present one year and she hid it. She said, there, she says, you've got to find your present - a little present - she says, I've hid it. We searched all over the house for it. Where do you think it w
as? In the five gallon cooking boiler. We looked up the chimney and all. I thought I saw it. I said I've see - it's up the chimney look. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 Mother said no, it isn't that's a bag of saltpetre. }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 That was for curing the pig when it was killed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you all go to chapel together on Christmas day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, if Christmas Day didn't come on Sunday we didn't have any special service.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you have any little party or any relatives coming on Christmas or was it just the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Just the family.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You didn't have any visiting?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you have any playing or singing or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Well, we used to play games - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 On Christmas Day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What sort of games?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Hide and seek and - and - we used to have a game of snakes and ladders if it was if it was wet day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 This was just the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you have any musical instruments in the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, only mouth organ. My brother used to play a mouth organ. No piano - no - nothing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was there anybody in the family who sang?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Only myself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You used to sing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Were you in the choir?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. But I used to sing - I remembered my sister-in-law when she used to come over to see my mother she always used to get me to sing they
 hymn Holy, Holy, because I could get up to such a top note and so clear.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did your mother sing at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, she was a very good singer.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I don't remember much about father singing. He - he hadn't used to sing at home much. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did your mother sing round the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Always singing. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you and your mother and any of the other sing together in a group ever?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You didn't have musical occasions together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was it just the one brother that played the mouth organ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 That's all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You mentioned snakes and ladders - did your parents join in that game?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. They bought a little set just for us children to play.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did they play any games with you ever?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Were there any books in the house at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
Yes. There was - mother used to buy little books for me and I remember one book in special. It was John the Gravedigger and it ended with the little girl asking the gravedigger - who'll dig your gra
ve when you die, John? That so touched the old gentleman he didn't know how to answer. I well remember the end of that book.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Where did she buy that book?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 She must have bought it off someone at the door.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Would it have been the same person that came round with the dresses - would he have books too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I shouldn't think so. I don't remember him having them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Any other books in the house - grown up books?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Not many.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you ever remember your mother or father reading anything - newspapers or books or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 They never bought a newspaper - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Were they both able to read?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 At that some people couldn't read.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 They couldn't read a lot could they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 They never bought a newspaper?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did they ever see a newspaper - did anyone lend them one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 They didn't read them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What about magazines?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Nothing like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Have you any recollection at all of either of them sitting reading?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Only the Bible.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When did they read the Bible?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Oh, very often - at night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 In the week as well as Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did they read it aloud?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Sometimes father would.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Would your mother ever read it aloud?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, and she'd mark it, you know. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Were you ever taken out visiting neighbours or friends or relations?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. Only used to go Sunday night for a walk. That was only outing - yes. Had the school outings. Bar the school outings.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 To get the prizes you mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What about going shopping - you were sent to Hook Norton - did you ever... ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Chipping Norton. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Were you ever actually taken out shopping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. Mother used to order her grocery once a month. That was delivered.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 There was no going to the shops at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, not very often. Only for small things.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 But your mother wouldn't take you to the shops to buy anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you ever remember going out with your parents on a Bank Holiday or for an outing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, never. No, never remembered my parents going. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Ever go away for a holiday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Never.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Your father was the steward at the chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What sort of chapel was that - what denomination?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 Wesleyan}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 . Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was that in }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 Wychford}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551  village?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, it was at Ascot. That was about half mile from the village. Was between Ascot and }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 Wychford}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did your parents go every Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Your mother and your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 My mother went every Sunday that she was able. Either in the afternoon or the evening.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 How often did your father go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
He used to go in the morning and light the stove fire and stay to the prayer meetings - make the fire up and come home and have his dinner and then go back in
 the afternoon service. Home and have his tea and then back to the evening service. I always used to have to go to Sunday school in the afternoon - stop to the service in the afternoon and just now and again in the summer time mother'd take us for a walk 
at night. If we'd been all together in the afternoon. But father never missed chapel.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 On a Sunday were you allowed to play games?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 How was Sunday kept them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Just - well, very, very - quiet.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did your parents think it wrong to work on a Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes. He wouldn't - my father wouldn't even have a bucket of water fetched from the fountain on the Sunday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 That meat pudding - was it done so that it could be prepared beforehand?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 That was usually prepared on Saturday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Would you not be allowed to do any sewing or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, nothing. Unless it were a very, very emergency - mother wouldn't think of doing any sewing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Were you allowed to sing and that kind of thing on Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, but - you could sing hymns - that's all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 On Saturday you used to go and fetch medicines sometimes for two or three peoples?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 That was also the day that you polished up the door knobs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. I had me work to do first.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was there anything else you used to do on Saturday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Only the - just the shoe cleaning and - chopping the wood and fetching the water, filling the red pan for Sunday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 But chopping the wood and fetching the water - that was for your own family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 So you didn't get paid for that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. That was my Saturday penny. I had to earn that Saturday penny.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 They gave you the Saturday penny?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. For that - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was there a Sunday school outing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. I remember we went to Broad
moor Lodge one year on the Sunday school outing. And I had a red - that red twill dress and I had a fall - I fell in - in a patch of -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You must have been upset about that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I was. I never forgot it. I could almost take you to the spot now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What did your mother say when you got back?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Oh, she grumbled but -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 She didn't punish you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Because she knew it was an accident?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 She - yes, yes. I felt terrible thought the remainder of the day 'cos it was all down the front of my dress.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Ruined your day I suppose?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Were there other Sunday school outings every year?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Each year there was one Sunday school outing. It - generally in the summer about this time of the year when we could have our tea in a
 field - somewhere.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Were there anniversaries at that chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Were those a big affair?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
Yes. They used to have the people from Chipping Norton, Hook Norton and that come to the chapel. Used to have a big tea party. Mother being cha
pel keeper she used to clean the chapel and - she used to get it ready for those meals 'cos one or two of her people used to help her with - get the teas and - and that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Were there recitations or singing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 We used to have a Sunday school anniversary when we used to say our recitations and singing and that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you do the recitations too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Used to say one - I can't remember -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 On your own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes. And sing on me own.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you enjoy that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Oh, we used to look forward to that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Were there any other social activities you remember in the chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 As far as I remember that's all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was there any temperance club attached to the chapel at all or anything in the village?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, there was a - there was a tem
perance club I think attached to the chapel because if you put your name - if you were a teetotaller you put your name down at chapel. You was enrolled as a member and that was all I remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You didn't have special parties or activities?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. I don't remember any - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Were you enrolled?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I wasn't teetotal. I used to get my -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Beer was a food to people in those days wasn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. I remember I used to have half a glass of beer - home brewed beer as I got older I could have half a glass.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What age would you be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Oh, thirteen or fourteen - after I left school.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You said your father always said grace at meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you ever have family prayers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did your father take an interest in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 All I remember he always used to vote Liberal. I don't remember anything more. He always used to vote - he always voted Liberal.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You don't know why he was Liberal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. I think he thought it was the working man's - part - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you know if your mother took an interest in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You don't remember her voting in 1918?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No, I don't remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 At that time some men thought they might lose their jobs if they didn't vote a certain way - 
do you know if any pressure was ever put on your father in that way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No I don't think so - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was he ever a member of the Liberal party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, he wasn't - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you remember him ever working for the Liberals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 He didn't work for them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You don't remember your mother or father taking part in any political activity?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No. I don't remember anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 How did they spend their time when they weren't working?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes. It was only evenings and they were glad to sit down and relax.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What would they do then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
Well, they didn't get - my father didn't very often get home 'til six o'clock at night. And by the time he'd had his wash and his meal it was getting on for bedtime.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did your mother have any interests at all outside the home and family - clubs or institutes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Nothing like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you know if your father ever went to a pub?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I remember him went to - he went to pub once. Just once I remember wh
en his brother came from Banbury. That's only time I ever remember him going to pub.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 My mother never went to pub. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you ever remember your father going to races?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Betting?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Nothings.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Would he have disapproved of that sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I think he would.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did he have any sporting activities of any kind?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, he never took part in anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 There was the doctors club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Medical club.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You said there was the club feast in June?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was that for that particular club or was that something else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
No, that was the club - they used to have a - a club where you paid - I don't know whether it was a shilling a year - to be a member and that was more or less a get together club. And then -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Wasn't there a benefit attached to it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
No. No benefit. And then in June they used to have the club feast. All the members used to assemble at ten o'clock in the morning on this particular day - go to church and then come up from church to the village school where there meal was prepared. }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 And then - they used to have races and swing boats and roundabouts and - bit of a fair in the green by the school.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When you say they went to church - wasn't that the chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. That was the church.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Could chapel people belong to it then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Anybody could go.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 But then you would go along to the church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes. Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was it not a Church of England service they'd have in the church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 It didn't matter - people didn't mind?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
No, they were - they weren't at all - you know - particular. Church-chapel people would go to church and - I think the church people might have gone to chapel I don't know.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 There wasn't much distinction made between the two then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Not much - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What sort of people went to the church - were they different in any way as a general rule from the chapel people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Well the farmers used to go to church - I don't remember many farmers going to chapel. Wa
s more or less the poorer working class people went to chapel more than to church.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What about people like the shoemaker or any }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 shop keeping}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551  people, where did they go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Some - some of them would go to church and one or two go to chapel.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 How did you get on with your brother Frederick and your other two brothers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
Well, my brother Frederick I got on very well with but the other two with them more or less - much older and I didn't have so much dealings with them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was there one brother you felt particularly close to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Oh, brother Fred was the next oldest after my sister died and he seemed to be nearer to me than the others.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Of your sisters was it Fanny that you felt particularly close to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes. She was next to me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What about the other sisters - how did you get on with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 They were married - they was in service and then married and away from home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Can you remember how you got}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551  on}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551  with them when they were at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Very well, I think - yes. We all seemed a very happy family to me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Who did you play with when you were a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Just my girl friend from across the way - the farmers daughter - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Anybody else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Sometimes another girl from across the way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you and your sister play together when she was alive?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Not much, because she wasn't very well, she was ailing I think for five years. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did she spend much time in bed then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No. She was able to get up and dress and be about up to the very last.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you ever play with brother Fred?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. He was at work. Yes. They went to work about eleven. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Whereabouts did you play when you played with your friend?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Just out in the street.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you ever play in the garden?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 In the rickyard we played. In our rickyard - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you play in your friends home at all?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
Sometimes we - I used to have my girl friend across the way and we used to go up in the attic and play with our dolls or anything wet days and we couldn't play out of doors.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Were there any other places you used to play?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I used to go across to her house sometimes and we used to play in the garden shed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What about in fields round about?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Would your mother have allowed you to if you'd wanted to stray far of off?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
I'd have had to have told her where I was going. Or have asked her if I could have gone. And if she told me I could go out to play for so long I had to be in. That was the time I'm afraid I might have had a bit of a hiding if I disobeyed her.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 She meant what she said didn't she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What games did you play - do you remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Hopscotch and - shuttlecock - cricket.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 The girls played cricket?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes, we - rounders and we used to play.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did boys play with girls in those games?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Sometimes but not very often.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you ever play marbles?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Sometimes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Were you allowed to get dirty when you played?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Well, not very dirty we didn't but I always had to change when I got home from school. Put my play clothes on.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you have a different pinafore to wear when you were playing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did your mother allow you to play with anyone you wanted to play with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 We lived at the end of the village and there was only abo
ut five house and - the girls round about - the only ones that I usually played with.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And your mother didn't have anything against you playing with all of those?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was it just the two you played with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Well, two or three. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you belong to any youth organisations?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No. Nothing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was there anything like that?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 There was a drum and fife band and my brother Fred joined that. That was all I remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Could a girl have joined that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, it was just for the boys.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You used to do quite a lot of jobs for your mother on Saturdays and that sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you have any other things to do - did you collect anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you keep any pets?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you have any hobbies?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Not as I ever remembers - nothing special.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you do any gardening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I had a little flower garden on my own. I used to look after that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What did you grow in it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Oh, I used to get the seeds and plant the seeds - a
ny seeds that I could find and mother would let me have and plant 'em. I thought it was wonderful - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You took quite a lot of care of it did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What sort of age were you when you started on the garden?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Oh about seven or eight.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 How long did you keep it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Up 'til the time I went to service after I left school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What happened to it then when you were away?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I think mother looked after it - just to keep it going for me 'cos she knew I took interest in it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you ever go fishing?
