\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 He'd offer it then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And you mentioned relatives coming to stay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Who were those relatives?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 My father's brother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was that Alfred?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 That was Alfred. He used to come once a year.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Anybody else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I used to have a cousin from St Neots - she used to come and stay for a - for a week or fortnight - when she had her holid
ays. Once a year - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Which relation was it that gave some money when they came?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 My cousin - from St Neots.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Who did she give the money to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Used to give it to me - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 How much?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Sometimes I'd have a shilling.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You must have been pleased?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Oh, I was thrilled.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Children appreciated things then didn't they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You used to go to your married sister for a week didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 How old were you when that started?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I should say about nine or ten. I had to look after her children while I was there - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You paid for your keep then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 How many children did she have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Nine.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When you first started going how many did she have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Four.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you go regularly to stay with her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Once a year - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Where was that?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Long Compton.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you enjoy it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. I always looked forward to going. I knew I had to work when I got back.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did going to your sister continue for many years?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Up to the time I went to service.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You stopped after that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you ever remember friends calling in casually without an invitation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 People didn't drop in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you remember if your parents called in on other people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
My father used to call in on a man on his way down to the chapel weekends just to see if he was going down to the chapel. And if he was they'd go together. Come back together. That's about all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 But it wasn't to sit and chat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 People often say in those days that they made their own amusements.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you ever remember your parents taking part in any activities like musical activities or games of any sort with other grown ups?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You mentioned that the poorer working class people went to the chapel mostly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What would you think the other classes were in the village at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What we'd call middle class. The farmers was about the best off. Except the Squire.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Any other classes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Well, the wheelwrights and carpenters - they would have - about on the level I think with the farmers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was there anything above that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. Only the Squire.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Just the Squire?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You considered him separate from the middle class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was there anybody else in his station of life in the village?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 He was sort of on his own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, he was more or less just the one and only.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Would you say that the working class people were al
l much the same or were there different standards of behaviour and living amongst them in the village?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 They all seemed about the same - they was all brought up the same in my idea.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 In some areas people talk about the difference between the rough and the respectable people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was it like that in your village then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, not - no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you remember making a difference between the craftsmen and the labourers in the village - did you feel there to be a difference in that
 way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, I don't think so - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Would you call a wheelwright a craftsman?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, he would be a - craftsman.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Which group would you say your family belonged to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Oh, the working class - yes. The poor.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 In that village then the farm labourers were all in that class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Who else would you say was in that working class? There weren't any factories?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, there was the blacksmith - he'd employ one boy and the wheelwright and carpenters perhaps they'd employ a la
d. The saddler he used to employ one man. The baker - they'd employ one man to do the - take the bread round.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 The people that they employed would be in a different class at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Well, they would be just a little bit different to the farm l
abourers although they associated with us. Everybody seemed to associate with one another that time of day. Yes. Never seemed no - no - }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 rowdyism}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551  like it is today. Rowdyism. No - it all seemed to be so quiet and calm and collected.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You said the baker employed somebody and there was that bit of difference - do you mean between the baker and the person he employed?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, there would be just that wee bit of difference - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Can you remember being brought up to treat people of one sort differentl
y from another in ways like toughing your cap or saying Sir or Madam?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
We had to say Sir to all - everyone above our standard. What we termed above our standard - even the baker had to say Sir to. I was always brought up to be polite to everyone.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 So you said Sir to the baker and the wheelwright those people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Would you call the Squire that?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. You'd have to curtsy. Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you remember calling anybody Madam? No. Was the Squire married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No. He had a housekeeper and it - she was Lady Abercrombie and - we used to have to say M'lady to her.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 To the housekeeper?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. When she brought the things to the school for distribution.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was she a housekeeper in the usual sense of the word?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 She was a Lady housekeeper as you might say. She didn't do any work or anything she was just in control of the running of the mansion.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was she a relation of his?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No relation.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And you called her }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 M'lady}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What about the bakers wife and people like that - how did you address them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You - just normally - you wouldn't -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Just Mrs you mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Not Madam?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you remember anybody saying Sir to your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Who do you think were the most important people in the village?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I don't know as there was anybody in particular - not particularly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Not the Squire even?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, well - didn't have much contact with him, you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was there a schoolmaster in the village?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Who did he associate with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 He didn't associate with many people at all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 He kept himself to himself did he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Him and his wife - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Why do you think that was?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I really wouldn't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was there a clergyman?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was there - what about the chapel - was that visiting people who came there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 There wasn't one set person?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Who did the clergyman mix with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 He used to go round the village and visit the sick.
 Find out if there was anyone needed any help. One clergyman we had - the one that sent me to the sanatorium at Weston - he was really wonderful good. Yes. All the time I was ill I always had my dinner sent down, every day. Nice hot meal.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 He was in contact a lot with people was he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes. He used to visit more than the others.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You knew several did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Can you remember anybody at that time say moving up from the working class to the middle class or down from the middl
e class to the working class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 People kept the same?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, they seemed to keep the same.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 If you heard somebody saying he's a real gentleman or she's a real lady what do you think they meant at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I should think they'd mean that they was people that would help you and do - do - do good to anybody.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I think it was the Earl of Camperdown that owned your house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you ever meet him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Who collected the rent then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 It used to be paid to the school - at school - collected by his agent - the land agent.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 But the agent didn't come to the door?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You took it to the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do your remember what your parents or yourself though about the landlord?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Never knew much about him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You didn't consider him either good or bad?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You told me that your parents had this little bit of money left to them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you think that they had a struggle to make ends meet though?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 They did before - yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You mentioned that you'd get a loaf or half a crown from the guardians or the parish.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did your parents have to make used of that at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Can you remember that or was it before you were old enough to remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Oh, I was about seven. I think, when they first applied for that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Why did they have to apply at that particular time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Oh because father had lost so much time from work and he hadn't been well and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was that because of the weather or because of his health?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Because of the weather and his health.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 The two together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you know what your mother and father felt about having to apply for that relief?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 They didn't like it. But they had to do it to keep - to keep on going.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you know how they felt the parish treated people at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Well, they - they made a rule you see for everybody to have the same - equal share Half a crown and a loaf. A large loaf that was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 It didn't matter what your circumstances were, you always got that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. You had the same - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did they ask your mother and father a lot of questions or inspect their house or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No. Never.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 They didn't do anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Can you remember exactly how it was your mother did apply - did she have to go and see somebody or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, she'd go and see the Rector or the Vicar - whichever was there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And she would tell him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 How old were you when you first went to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Five. Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you go just the mornings or for the whole day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Whole day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was it a church school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Church of England school - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was it mixed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Mixed - yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was it mixed right through?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Boys and girls in the same class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, right through.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 How did you get to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Walked. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 How long did it take?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 About ten minutes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did anybody go with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What did you think about school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I enjoyed ever minute - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Why do you think that was?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I don't know, I took to school and I learned by lessons and I was good really at although I say it, I was good at everything at school.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 How did you feel about the teachers there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I only remember one teacher - Mr Jeffrey.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was that the schoolmaster?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did he have any assistants?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 His wife used to come in and teach the infants. In the infant school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 But otherwise it was just him was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 How many of you were there altogether?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I should say about fifty altogether.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And he taught all of you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You must have kept quite quiet then?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, we had to. If we was heard talking it was outside - out the game. I remember my girl friend getting me the cane once.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Any other times or just once?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Only the once that -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 That was for talking was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 She said I was talking. The schoolmaster used to go indoors and have a drink in the summertime
 and he came back in and he said all those talking come outside. 'Course I hadn't been talking - I didn't go out. My friend put - she was a little bit annoyed with me I think - she put her hand up and she said please Sir, Florrie Stow was talking. And he 
called me out and he - he thought I was talking and so he said for not owning up and going out when I was told to he gave me two stripes - I had the cane on each hand.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What did you say to your girl friend about that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I didn't speak to her for a week or two.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What did your teacher say was important in life - did he tell you what he wanted you to be in school and in life generally?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No. He left us to - sort our own things out I think. Sort our - everything out for ourselves.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you remember if he made a particular point about manners or tidiness?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Everything had got to be put back in its place. And very punctual. Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 He was very keen about punctuality?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Very keen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What about the way you spoke and that sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Always used to have to say yes Sir, no Sir.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What about your general manners and way of behaving and that sort of thing - did he concentrate much on that in school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. He always taught us to be polite, you know, to everyone.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You mentioned getting the cane - were there any other punishments he would give?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Not to the girls.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What about the boys?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Sometimes he'd give them the cane across the behind.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 But the girls got it on the hand?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Would you say he punished a lot or not so much?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 He was pretty severe really - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You only got it once?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I only got it once on the two hands. Sometimes -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you get it once on the one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 For what sort of things did he punish you then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Sometimes if I didn't do my writing right I had to go out have the cane.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What about if you got a sum wrong - that sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 How often say in a week would you get it on the hand?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Oh, I might go a month I've not had it. Yes, not have it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did your parents take an interest in your work at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 They never see it. We never took any books home, we never had any homework or anything like that. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did they ask you how you were getting on or talk about school at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Sometimes mother would.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What sort of things would she be interested in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 She'd ask me what I'd been doing and - what I liked best.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did they ever go up to the school for an open day or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did they ever meet your teacher - did they know him personally?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, they knew him as a - a - village resident like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did he go to the chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, he used to go to church.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 But they didn't meet him at the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 At that school did the children come from similar types of home to your own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Would you say that the schoolmaster singled out some children for different sort of treatment from others?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 He didn't?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 He wasn't down on certain children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No favourites?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 So many do don't they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, they do one-half.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Were there any little gangs or cliques or groups in the school?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Only in playtime.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you remember any children who were left out of things - alone?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, no. If they didn't want to play they'd say oh I'd rather not play and they just stand around or do what they wanted.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 There were no children who were sort of outcasts?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you have any children coming from the workhouse to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you ever go to any other school after that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When you were thirteen after two years in standard seven you left.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you think if you could have stayed longer you would have done?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Had you learned all there was to learn at that school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes. That was why I was in standard seven for two years. They couldn't advance me any farther.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you have any regrets about your education?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you think you }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 benefited}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551  from attending school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, I do. I think I benefited a lot really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You certainly write very well and they were keen on spelling in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I don't expect you had a great deal of trouble with spelling did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You told me about earning that Saturday penny - did you ever have any other means of earning money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When I went to fetch the medicine - that was all. Yes. That was the only time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Your first full time job was as kitchen maid?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 At the house of the banker?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was the bank actually adjoining the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 It was in the house - it was - the - underneath the house - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 On the ground floor?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, on the ground floor.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Like when people keep a shop and live above?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Can you tell me how you got this job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 It'd be my brother's wife's sister was cook there. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Which brother was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Brother Will. Older brother. His wife's sister was cook there and 
she knew they was requiring a kitchen maid and so she let me know and mother took me down and had an interview.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Who did you meet when you went there then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I met the cook first and then the lady of the house. And it was arranged that I should go up for trial for a month.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When you met the lady of the house did she ask you many questions and that kind of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Not very many. \{ILLEGIBLE\} No. You had to have two references. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And who were your referees then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 The schoolmaster gave me one and the Rector gave me the other.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What were your hours of work at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 About half past seven in the morning to about nine at night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No half days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I had a half day week there - at the first place - yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What time would your half day start?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 After I'd cleared away and washed up the mid-day meal.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Which was about what time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 About two - two to half past.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And you had to be in at I think... ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Back in at eight o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 She made a special point of that didn't she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You were paid seven and eight a month?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you feel at the time that that was a fair wage or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 It was - considering the wages of other people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 So you didn't feel you were being unfairly treated?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You gave some of it to your mother for clothes?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
I used to send six shillings out of the seven and eightpence a month to repay her for the clothes and outfits she'd bought me to start service with.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 How did you spend the money you kept yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 On sweets. And that would last a month - one and eightpence. That one and eight had to last a month.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 At that place there was the cook and yourself - were there any other servants employed there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Nobody else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. We used to have a woman in for the washing now and then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No men or boys employed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Where did you sleep there - did you have a room to yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Whereabouts was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Up in the attic.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Where did you eat your meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 In the kitchen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was there a servants hall or anything of that type?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did the lady of the house supervise all housework personally?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. The cook used to give my orders. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you feel at case with the cook - did you get on with her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, fairly well - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was she a good deal older than you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What about your employer - did she have a family as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, they had no family.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Just her and her husband?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 That's right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you feel at ease with her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
Didn't see much of her. Because I was kitchen maid then you see - the lady of the house always made it a rule to give their orders to the cook or the house - keeper by nine in the morning - they didn
't enter the kitchen after - without asking the cook if they could come in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 It was the cooks province?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 So you didn't really come into contact with her then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Can you remember on any occasions if you did come into contact how you felt with her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I don't remember - much. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What did you call her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Madam.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What did she call you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Mary I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Why did she call you Mary?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Most of the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 maids}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551  was called Mary that time of day. No matter what your name was. It was Mary - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did that bother you at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Didn't worry you not being called Florrie?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What did you call the cook?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Just called her by her name.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Her first name?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And she called you Mary too did she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I thought she might have called you Florrie as you were almost like a relations but she didn't?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you feel that she took an interest in you as a person?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 She helped me a lot - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did she talk to you much about anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Not really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 She wasn't that sort of person?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Would you say that the lady of the house was interested in you as a person?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I don't think she took any particular interest as long as our work was done. That was all that mattered really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You don't remember her ever giving you any advice about anything or telling you how you ought to live?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Some Mistresses used to I believe at that time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 But she wasn't like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When you went out where did you go for your half day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You used to be able to get home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 How long did it take you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 About half an hour.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 How did you go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Walked. Everywhere.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 If your mother hadn't wanted you to be back by eight o'clock what time do you think she would have said you should be back?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 My mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, your mother wanted you back at eight didn't she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What would the lady's rule have been if your mother hadn't been the type to care?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Oh perhaps - perhaps half past nine or ten o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did she enquire what you did when you went out - did she make it any concern of hers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 The lady of the house? No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you remember feeling homesick?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
I did when I first went - first week I was there. Cook used to - turn and console me and say you'll settle down. Don't worry. And I did settle down.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 About how long did it take for you to settle?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 About a fortnight.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Would you say that you were lonely in that job or did you have enough companion-ship from the cook?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Well I didn't have a lot of companionship - in my girlhood days except my girl friends around so I didn't feel all that lonely.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was there anything in that job that you particularly liked?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, not in that job.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was there anything you particularly disliked about the situation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Can remember something about your routine in that house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, I was in the kitchen most of the time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What did you do there in the kitchen in the morning for example?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Oh all this - dirty work. And - prepare - oh used to have to light the fire and do the range and - clean the shoes and - do -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Would you clean the cooks shoes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. And all the shoes had to be put outside the bedroom doors in the morning.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When the cook got the breakfast what did you do to help her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Fetch and carry. Yes, and lay the breakfast table.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Then the family would have breakfast?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did anybody wait on then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I used to sometimes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When they'd finished what would you do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When they'd left the table I'd clear the table and then go and set to and wash up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you do that unaided?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And after that was done what was the next thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
They used to have their mid-day meal cooked and then have their tea at tea time - there was no late dinners at that time of day unless it was just the very, very high class like the Squire or that. They - they used to h
ave their meal - main meal at middle day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What sort of time was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 About half past twelve to one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When did you have your breakfast?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I always had my breakfast while the Mistress and Master was having theirs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you eat with the cook?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You sat down together with her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did the master and mistress have their meal together in the morning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did the Mistress come down for breakfast?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Always.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What sort of food did they have for breakfast?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 About the same as you would have now. They'd have }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 porridge}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551  - oatmeal porridge mostly. And fried breakfast.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did they ever have anything different on Sundays for example?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 There was just the range for cooking on was there in that house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did they eat in the dining room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 A woman came in to do the washing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Washing wasn't sent out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did the Mistress make and mend the clothes there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I don't know - I don't remember - don't remember. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did she ever do any cooking herself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you know who was responsible for repairs to the house there and improvements to the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, don't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What sort of age were they when you went there - were they elderly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 About forty to fifty. Yes, middle age.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When you'd have your breakfast and cleared away and washed up what was the next thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 We used to get the vegetables ready for cook. And - perhaps have to cle
an the silver or something like that. Get the wood and coal in, you know, for the house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What about cleaning in the rest of the house - did you do that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Well, I had to do - the most of the cleaning because there was no other maid. Cook used to help do some of the dusting. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you have certain rooms to do on certain days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Can you remember anything about that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Nothing particular - no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 But you were responsible for cleaning the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 How many rooms were there then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Five. Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Including the kitchen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 So it wasn't such a big place?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Oh - five bedrooms. Yes. Five bedrooms. Dining room and sitting room and kitchen and scullery.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 That's a lot for a thirteen year old girl isn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you do most of it on your own or did cook share the work of it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 She used to do the light work - the cook - the dusting and that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you have any floors to scrub there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Well, not really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You didn't have to scrub the kitchen floor?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Oh yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
When you'd got the food ready for her and done your jobs and things like that did you actually help her with the cooking - just the fetching and carrying was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 That's right - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And you waited at table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And when did you eat your mid-day dinner?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
After - after I'd waited at table and served the first course I used to have mine and then when they had the second course took in I used to serve that and then come back in the kitchen and have my second course.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What did you do in the afternoon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Well there's very often odd jobs to do - window cleaning or silver or things like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You didn't have any time off in the afternoon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Not away from the house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you have any sort of a slack time where you could sit down?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 That was considered the right thing was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 How long would that be about?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Oh, about half an hour.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Not very long?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 If caller came to the door did you have to answer the bell?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you change in the afternoon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What did you change into?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 We had to wear a print dress and a white apron in the morning - a plain white apron.
 And in the afternoon we used to put on a clean cap and black dress and a white apron with a needlework top - lace and that round the top.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Had your mother provided those for you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Six of everything. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did she make them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Make them all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When you }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 opened}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551  the door to people and that sort of thing did you serve afternoon tea to callers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, not very often. Didn't entertain very much in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 She didn't have an at home day or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What time did they have their tea?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Half past four - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What sort of things did the cook do for their tea?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Nothing special - only bread and butter and jam or - and cakes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 They didn't have cold meat or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 So it was a similar tea to what You'd have been used to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes, it was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did they have anything else later on in the day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 They used to have a light supper - served at eight o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And that was something you hadn't been used to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I hadn't been used to it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you have that too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What sort of food would they have then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Biscuits and cup of milk or - cocoa.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Nothing else?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, not there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You helped cook get the tea ready did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you do it on your own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I used to have to get the tea on my own - lay the table.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Where was cook then while you were getting the tea ready?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I don't remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 She didn't really have any cooking then after mid-day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, she didn't. No, she didn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When you'd done the tea did you wash up on your own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What was the next stage then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I didn't have much to do after tea. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 So up }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 till}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
 eight 'o'clock supper time what sort of things would you do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Read a book. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you go to your own room then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Would you have been allowed to if you'd wanted to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. If I was on call. Yes, if I was anywhere that I could hear the bell it was all -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 It didn't matter where you were as long as you heard the bell?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. If they wanted me they'd ring the bell in the - whichever room they were in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Your attic room wasn't wired for a bell was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 So you really had to be near the bell?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was any jam or bread made in that household?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Bottling of fruit or vegetables?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Never. Never heard of. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did the cook make any pickles?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I don't remember - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What about home brewed beer and wine?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Never. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you remember the lady making any medicines?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Were the vegetables bought or grown?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Bought. They hadn't much garden.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did they provide any of their own fruit and vegetables?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I think they had a few raspberries.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 In your own home your mother didn't like tinned food.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you remember anything like that in your first job? No? And this garden that they did have who used to work there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 They used to have a man from out of the town come in and do it for them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did they keep any livestock?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 How many times a week did they eat meat? Every day would it be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And breakfast too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you have the same food as your employer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
