\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
No. When I used to serve the first course I always used to have to take cooks and my plate in and our food was cut and put on the plate to b
ring out after I'd served the table. It was usually put in the oven to keep hot. Until I'd served the second course and come out to have our own.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did she consult you as to what you wanted to have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, she would ask me if there was anything I didn't like so - but I was fairly good with - in that respect.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You weren't faddy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 If you wanted a second helping what would happen then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Well, I don't know as I should have had it. I think they used to give you enough on the plate - what they thought was sufficient.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you remember ever asking for a second helping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par 
