\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Whereabouts was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 That was a mile and a half from my home. It was a lone farm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Nothing else round about you mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Why was it that you went there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
For one thing it was near home and - we knew the farmer and his wife very well. And - I thought I'd - try - like to try it. And when this general }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 maid}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551  there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And you had eight and four a month?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When you went there you had all these duties to do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Were there any children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No, they was old people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Had they had children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. Never had any.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You say these were the maids pride of the kitchen... 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 That was the brasses and the -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was there another maid besides you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. I was maid of all works - master of none.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 So when you say these were the maids pride of her kitchen you were referring to yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes, yes. Any household that had the brass and that that was the kitchen maids pride.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 To keep them shining?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Were there any other servants at that job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Nobody at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I was the only maid there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did anybody come in and do the garden there or washing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 We used to have a woman for the washing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did she iron as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 So you didn't have to concern yourself with that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did the Mistress supervise you in your work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. She gave my orders and I knew from day to day what I had to do, it was in rotation.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 How did you get along with her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Very well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What sort of person was she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Very homely. Very nice person.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You'd known her quite a long time had you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did she also call you Mary?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you call her Madam too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you feel that she was interested in you as a person.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, I think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 More than any other place?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did she give you any general advice about your behaviour or dress or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 She wouldn't have needed to would she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, no. No, no. She was wonderful good to my mother. She used to send her pats of butter up - dripping - anything like that - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When you were there did you also come back at eight o'clock?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What time do you think was the usual thing for general servants?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I might have stayed out }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 till}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551  half past nine or ten there if - if mother'd let me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Why do you think your mother felt that about the time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I think she was anxious that I should - you know, keep - that -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Were you also homesick there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Were you lonely there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Would you say there was anything there you particularly liked or disliked?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
I hadn't used to like to have to scrub the - the milk buckets. I used to have to do them with whitening and the sifted ash. Scour them first and them put them in the bath of water and scald them. I used to hate that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Why?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I don't know - it - its thing I didn't like doing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 In that house did you do all the cooking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did she not do any at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 She used to come in and supervise sometimes - just have a look at the joint an
d see if it was all right - especially if I was doing any other work around the house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you remember her mending or did you have to do the mending of the clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 She would do the mending. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you remember her doing sewing at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, she'd do her sewing and darning.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You didn't have to do anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No. Only me own.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 At that house where did they eat their meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 In the dining room. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Where did you have yours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 In the kitchen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you have a range there as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Can you tell me - did she also give you your food on your plate and out it up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 They used to cut the meat and serve - and let me have the meat in the kitchen. But I had my own vegetable. Helped myself
 to vegetable. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you have the same food as they had?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No difference?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did they also have their tea at four thirty?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did they have a supper at night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Always had bread and milk at supper. Th
ey did. Yes. She used to have sugar in hers and the Master used to have salt and pepper in his. Bowl of bread and milk - every - every night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you have the same?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 If I wanted it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did she ask you to make bread there and jam?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. She used to make the jam - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And bread?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Not very often - no,
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What about pickling and making wine?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 She'd make the pickles - yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And brewing and wine making?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Nothing of that type?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No medicines?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did they also have a very small garden or did they have more space there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 They had more garden there. They grew more - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you remember them buying the vegetables and fruit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No, this - I think they were self supporting.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Like you had been in your own home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was it the same there that you don't remember tinned food?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, I - there wasn't much tinned food in the country. No. I can only remember syrup being sold in tins.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did they keep - did they have hens?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And pigs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. I used to have to look the eggs up.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Were you with them on Christmas Day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I went home on Christmas Day. Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What time of the day were you allowed home then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 About two o'clock - yes, after dinner.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And you came back at eight again?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Always eight?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Always before eight. Sometimes mother'd come half way back with me. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you remember if they had any musical instruments?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, no they didn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 They weren't musical?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 At that house did you also read their books?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes. I had one or two of me own there - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Where did you get your books - did you buy them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you remember them reading newspapers or magazines?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 They used to have a magazine - I rem - I don't remember the name.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 While you were there was there a funeral at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you go away with them anywhere?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you ever in any of your situations go away with the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No. I never remember they going away.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 People weren't gadding about so much then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did they keep Sunday as a day of rest?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, always.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did that apply to you to - were you expected to do less on Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did they have a hot dinner on Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You had to prepare that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did they go to church or chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Master used to go to church now and again but the Mistress wouldn't - well, she didn't enjoy very good health and so she didn't go.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What about you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I used to go up home to this chapel in the afternoons sometimes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 It must have been nice going to the one you were used to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you remember there whether they had family prayers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you remember there if they took an interest in politics or didn't you know about that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Can you remember anything - did she go out to whist drives?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. Never.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 She was more like your mother in her life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes, yes. Never seemed to go out anywhere.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did the Master go out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 He used to go to market every Friday. Take the butter or anything else he'd got to supply - eggs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you ever go with him to help at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Never - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Would you have liked to have gone?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, I think I would but I never was ....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 So it was more a life at home in those days wasn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did they entertain and have people coming in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Never. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 She didn't have a day for callers or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When you were making beds and things like that did she help you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 She used to make her own bed and I just had the bedrooms to do - that was all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Can you remember anybody coming to stay there while you were there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, I can't no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You think they didn't?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You'd known these before hadn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes. I'd heard of them all my life time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 They'd known you all your life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Would you say they seemed familiar sort of people - they didn't seem different or strange in any way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, no. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 The second farmhouse place you had was after your time at Weston-Super-Mare?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Before - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You had four places before you went there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, I had three. The last place was the doctors. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 
And I went from the doctors to the Weston-Super-Mare and I only went back to help the lady at the farmhouse after - for a little while they were moving into the village.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And that lady you went back to help - that was a new place, you hadn't been there before?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, that was the second - second farm. Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 So what was the other farm house then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 The other farmhouse was at Broughton Rounds by Banbury.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you go there before the doctors?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Before the doctors.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 That was the one where the lady used to drink a lot?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 The second farmhouse. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I wonder if you'd mind telling me again about that time you had too much to drink?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 It was a hot summers da
y and she'd had - she'd been on the drink in the morning. Yes. And she asked me to go down in the cellar and fetch her a glass - a bottle of lemonade. I fetched this bottle of lemonade - she poured herself a drink of burgundy and lemon - she asked me if I
'
d like a drink. I thought well I'd try it. I said yes please. She poured me out a glass and I drunk it down I think perhaps rather too quick. She said go and fetch another bottle of lemonade Mary. So I fetched another bottle - she poured herself another g
l
ass of burgundy and lemon - asked me if I'd like one. I said yes please, not thinking what it would do for me. The result was in about half an hour she had to get me to bed with a very bad headache she told the master. Of course next morning when he came 
t
o knock at my bedroom door to call me up he said Mary, he says, how is your headache this morning. I said better thank you Sir. And that was - I remembered when I went to bed when the Mistress had got me to bed that I'd got the alarm clock on the side of 
the table - everything was going round in the room - I got in a state.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you tell your mother or anyone about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Oh, I told mother about it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What did she say?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Well, she said, she blamed the lady. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 She said she shouldn't have given it
 me. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 She knew very well that I wasn't used to anything like that. That - she was very cross about it.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did she say anything to the lady?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. She didn't like to.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When she took that place did she have any suspicions that the Mistress drank?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 She didn't know then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
No. I remember once the - he used - the farmer used to have family prayers and we were at prayers one morning and it's - whether she'd had any drink I don't know early one - in the middle of prayers she says - John
, she said - it's about time you got the men in that curlock, she said it's a disgrace. In the middle of the prayer - prayers. Said John, it's about time you got the men in the curlock - that was hoeing in the wheat. And she said, it's a disgrace.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Right in the middle of prayers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 So what did he say?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
Well, he got up and he went out and he didn't come back to dinner and - when I got up next morning Mistress's dress and coat and shoes was all hung on the back of a chair in the kitchen
 soaking wet through. And I thought well, I wonder if the Missus had tried to drown herself. I was so confused. And she didn't say anything when she got up - not - what had made her dress and that wet and - later }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 in}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551  the day she said I'm going to Banbury to
 my sons. She said if the Master comes back you tell him where I am and give him this note. And - I found out the Master had gone that day after prayers - he must have gone over to Twyford to a friend of his and he stayed there the night and she'd been lo
oking in the fields and in the wet grass in the fields - that's what made her dress and that wet through. Thinking as he perhaps wandered off.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did he come back after that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 He didn't come back for a week. And when he came back she was gone. She wa
s gone to Banbury - she left in the farmhouse on my own for a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And you were very young still?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes I was. About eighteen - eighteen to nineteen. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did the farm labourers have to have food given them and that sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No, they - farm labourers used to bring their own food.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 But you had to look after the calves didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes, there was the cows to feed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 They left you and trusted you to do all this on your own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes. And the butter making.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When she went off did she tell you when she was coming back?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
No. No. Just left there not, knowing who was coming back first or where they - where the Master was gone I didn't know. But he came back first.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did people come and enquire where they were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No. It was a lone....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Don't you think other people knew then?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 It was a lonely house - I don't think any of out - outside villagers knew anything about it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Were you nervous being there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, I never seemed nervous - no. And things were different then from what they were now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 After they came back did you stay long in that place?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You didn't think of giving notice or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. Not for a long, long time. I had inflammation in my eyes a
nd that was the reason really why I left. Mother wouldn't let me stay any longer. I didn't tell her I had to feed the calves in the morning but somebody from our village was doing some work nearby and - he happened to go and see my father and he said - Be
n
jamin, he said, I wouldn't let a daughter of mine, he said, be in service at Broughton Grounds. And father said why? Well, he said, I see your daughter, he said, out - out in the garden - yard feeding the calves this morning, he said - and that ain't a gi
rls job. That'd be about seven o'clock you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 So what did your father say then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Well, I think he talked it over with mother and then she advised me to leave and get another place.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Girls didn't usually have to feed calves if they were in service?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, not really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Why do you think he thought it was particularly wrong that you should have done it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Well, I believe father thought I caught my inflammation in my eyes through being in the wet grass in the morning feeding the calves.
 They were fed in the orchard you see, where the grass was quite long.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Were there any children in that house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No. They only had one son and he was married and lived at Banbury. That's where she went off to.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And you said the place was much the same as the other farmhouse?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, for work - for the housework - yes, much the same - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you have all those other extra things like washing out all those pails?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, everything to do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was much the same?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Then you went to the doctors - I think you had eight and four a week at the first farmhouse?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And at the second farmhouse how much did you have there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Nine and eightpence.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And what about the doctors?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I had fifteen and fourpence I think. I think it was.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And did you keep on giving money to your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Not after I - not after I'd paid for my clothes. I put it in a bank.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you remember what job you were at when you finished paying for your clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I think I must have finished paying for my clothes when I was at my first farm-house. Place.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 After that you banked it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you bank a regular amount every month?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. Perhaps I'd - I'd - well, what I could manage really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 While you were banking it did you have any special purpose in mind that you thought you'd use it for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Well, I was hoping to have it to get married some day. Have a home of me own.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was that a usual thing for young girls to do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 At the doctors can you remember anything particular about it - the ways it differed from the other jobs or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Well, instead of dairy work you see there was the surgery and the door to answer for the surgery calls and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did that take up much of your time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
Well in the mornings - yes. And they had two sons home - and they were home the weekends and they was Oxford - at college or somewhere in the week days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Were there any other servants there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. They had the daily woman in to do the - help do the cooking.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did she do house cleaning as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, not much. Helped with the cooking.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What were the doctor and his wife like?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 They were very good. Really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did she supervise you personally?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did she talk to you about anything very much - did you have much contact with her?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
No, not much. They didn't seem to in those days. They just kept you at - in your position like - treated you as a maid - some people were nicer to get on with than the others but - as a rule you just kept your position as a maid and that's it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Were you called Mary there too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Would you remember anything about the work of the house - making beer and bread and wine and jam?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 They never made any wine or anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 At that job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. They made some jam I think once - }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 raspberry}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551  jam.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What about bread - did they make bread there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When they made the jam was it the mistress who made it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 The woman that came in used to make it. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 
She come in the - stay on in the afternoon and make it. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 If there was anything special to be done like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was she a woman with her own family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes, she'd got three or four children.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did they also have a hot dinner at mid-day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, it was - late - six o'clock dinner - yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What did they have at mid-day then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Well, cold meats - salad or anything that was going.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did they have a supper later?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What did they have then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Oh just - drop of wine perhaps and biscuit. Nothing much - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 If they had a pudding what meal would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 At - late. Yes, with the late meal.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you eat with the lady who came in daily?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I had my meals with her - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did they cut the meat like they have in the other places?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What about vegetables?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 They had to buy most of their vegetables - they hadn't much garden there. They used to entertain quite a lot. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you remember people coming to stay there as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I remember when they had visitors and they had the sons home as well. They used to put me out to sleep to a friend of }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 theirs}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And somebody took your room then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. One of lads used to have my room.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What sort of entertainments did they have then - dinner parties?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
Well they used to have people to stay a week - a fortnight at a time. And the lady - sometimes she'd go to Germany for a month - the doctors wife. They'd have friends from Germany over here.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Had you met German people before?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 They spoke English?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 They spoke very well - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 How did they treat you, the people that came to stay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Very well, I think. I always had a good tip - yes. Yes. That was wonderful in those days. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Would you say at the doctors house you met people of a kind you hadn't met before?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
Yes, I think so. And I met my first boy friend there. Yes. I met my first boyfriend there one Sunday - I was allowed out from half past two to eight o'clock. And one Su
nday afternoon I had to lay the tea before I went out - they was having a party to tea. They'd got their best china tea service and the old-other one as well. I laid the table and I was just taking a tray of - their best tea service in on a tray and looke
d
 out of the window and saw my boy friend waiting for me on the bridge just down the road. They'd got some chairs with a little bit sticking out up the side, little bit higher than these, and I wore a dress similar to that one with a cuff that opened up he
r
e. Well, as I went to put the tray on the table my - the open part of my cuff caught in the top of the chair and sent the tray on the floor. Well, it broke - it broke and chipped most all of it. Oh she was in a state - oh she did carry on - she said I was
 mad to have boyfriend.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 She realised he was out there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
Yes. She realised they were there and she thought I was neglectful. She said I'd have to pay for a new set. And I said I would if she let it stop at that. But I wouldn't - I didn't want to be
 reminded what I'd done all the time - if I was going to buy a new set I wanted the matter closed. She did close the matter and I got - ordered a new set of - just the same as that one from Chapman's of Banbury. But before that was delivered - they had ha
ve it made special because that set came from Germany I think, somebody had presented it to her, it had got a lot of little red roses round the outside of the plates and that. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 
And - I had to leave there - I went home ill - before that was delivered and when
 it was delivered, Chapman's sent me the bill - I think it was thirty shilling - for eighteen or twenty-two piece - I don't - sure, whether it were sugar basin, cream jug - anyway, I paid the bill.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 From your savings was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. I took the mon
ey out the bank and I paid the bill and then I sent a letter asking her if she would pack the remainder of that set that was chipped and cracked and I'd collect it when I was able to. She wrote back and said I couldn't have it. But anyway -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You mean you were giving her a complete new set and she wasn't prepared to give you what was left of the old one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 New set - I paid - what was damaged and that but I did have it. I did have it. I went to see her after I was been to the }{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 sanatorium}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551  and was got be
tter I went to see her and I told her I said I shall take that, I said, that is mine, I've replaced yours at my own expense. Oh, she couldn't say much - she let me have it. There was six - six small plates they were all chipped but they weren't fussy in t
hose days like they are today. I - I mean they were hygienic as they are now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You were right to stand up for yourself there weren't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When they decided to send you to the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 sanatorium}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551  was it your village Vicar who paid for that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You said you had quite a nice time there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. I did. I really enjoyed it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 That boyfriend on the bridge - where had you met him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I met him in the village when I was out walking one Sunday afternoon.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And that village was ...?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Adderbury. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you go out with him regularly?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.-
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was he the one that didn't want to wait so long?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 While you were there did you make any other new friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you ever make any other girl friends besides the farmers daughter?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you mean after I'd been to service? Not very often. I used to go home as often as I could.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 That was your first boyfriend was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you meet his family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did your mother meet him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. He used to come every week - regular. Stop the night - used to come Saturday and cycle stop the night and back Sunday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Were you allowed to see him on your own and go out on your own and that sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. I could.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Of course you were independent really weren't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What sort of things did you do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Just went for walks. There was no shops or anything much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You said that when a Squire owned a village for an unmarried girl to have a baby was a very unusual thing in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, it was - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did the Squire own the village where you were - }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 Wychford}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 ?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes, he owned most of the village - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 But you think it was different in villages where the Squire didn't own it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Probably.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 In those days you hear about people making rough music - do you remember that at all? Does it mean anything to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 It was what they used to do sometimes if people in a village disapproved of the way some
body was behaving - say a man had beaten his wife or was carrying on with another woman or something - they would get together, a whole group of them and you've heard about that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes. They'd make an effigy of the person concerned and carry it up the streets and then they'd set fire to it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you remember that happening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. I remember that happening.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Oh, I was about ten or eleven.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And do you know why it was they did it in this particular case?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, I don't. It was a man - and I remember it was a man. He must have done something out of the ordinary, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you remember if there was a noise as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Oh yes, they'd - they'd have anything they could - trays or - or kettles or anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And do you remember what happened to this man as a result of this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I don't remember. I dare say he'd clear off out of the village. I think that was the idea. I should think that's what he would do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you remember this happening again later in your life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, no, I don't ever remember it happening but the once in our village. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Since the first world war have you done any jobs? I know you sold minerals for a while to make money didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, that was - just after we were married.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 So that was before the first world war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And you also made a little money collecting acorns and blackcurrants or black-berries?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes. We had - we had to - to live.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You used to also do a little bit of hair cutting?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Always cut the hair for all the family and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And you used to shave somebody who had nervous trouble didn't you?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes, I - shaved a very old man at Ascot-under-}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 Wychford}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What did he pay you for that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Threeha'pence. Threeha'pence haircut - threeh'pence - threepence for a shave and haircut.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was there anybody else you used to shave and do haircutting for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I'd do it for anybody that asked me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did quite a few people ask you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 The girls - girls - it was fashionable then - started the fashion with have their hair cut short.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 In the 1920's was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
Yes. And the girls used to come and ask me if I'd cut their head - I'd cut their hair. And I cut my hubbies and my families hair - oh up to 1950. Perhaps later.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you do any other sort of paid work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
What when I first - when I was first married as I sold those minerals I used to go out in the field - hoeing if I could get a job with any farmer. Then we moved down in the village and we a
fter moved down in the village I had my first babe and I couldn't go out then very much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you ever go out for any kind of job after you had children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I used to go out in the field - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was that seasonal work - a few weeks at a time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes. Hoeing generally.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you ever do any domestic work again?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. Not to go back - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Only that bit of extra field work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 That's right - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When you were doing your time in service before you were married did you ever think you would have liked another job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. I seemed quite content in service. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you ever belong to anything like a trade union?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you feel when you were working in the fields that there was a division between their workers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Would you say that when you went out to work that it changed your attitude to life in any way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, I don't think so, no. I used to enjoy it. It used to be a treat really to go out in a field. Yes. I used to like it - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Why do you think you enjoyed it?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Well, it was as change from every day hum-drum of the kitchen I think - the housework.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Company too of course isn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When you went to your first job did it change your relationship with your parents? Or towards your brothers and sisters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, I think it brought me a little bit }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 closer}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551  - yes, I think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 How was that do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Well, I was away from home you see and then when I did go home I felt - I felt much happier
 to go home and see my parents just for the day - or half day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did it change your feeling about your brothers and sisters at all do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Not much - because they were so much older.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you take an interest in politics up }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 till}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551  the time you got married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Your mother kept your little garden on for you didn't she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you ever do it when you went home on your off days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, I used to look after it - just see if there was any weeds or anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You were married in 1911?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 How long had you known your husband when you married him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 About six months.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Where did you meet him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I was helping pack up at the farmhouse where the people was moving. This was after I'd been to Weston-
Super-Mare. I was helping another girl and she had a boyfriend. She said to me she said, will you come out with me Sunday. And I said why? Well, she says, I'm going out with }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 Charles}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551  and if you like she said I'll ask him to bring a boy friend for you. I sai
d all right then. We arranged to meet the Sunday afternoon and as it happened this boyfriend of hers bought my hubby. And - she - she introduced us and from then - we - you know made arrangements and met and that was really how I first met him and went ou
t with him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Where did he come from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 He came from a village four miles away. Vales.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Where you later lived?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Where the doctor lived - yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You had been banking money hadn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Had he also saved before?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did your parents help you in setting up your home at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 They had to.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You'd known him about six months when you got married?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was it quite soon that you decided you would get married - would you say you had an engagement or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You had this wedding cake that cost six and six?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And it was four pounds?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, four pound in weight.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Could you describe the wedding to me?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Well, we just had our - the family. I sh
ould say about twenty to thirty people. And it was usual at that time of day to have a plum pudding like they do at Christmas, you know, the Christmas pudding. Oh, it wasn't a wedding without a plum pudding.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 A hot one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. We had a hot meal - beef and father cooked a half ham - home cured ham.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 One of your own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Where did the guests all sit and eat then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Oh, in the two sitting rooms - at home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 At your own home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You didn't have any friends - it was all family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And that was after the marriage at the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 Wychford}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551  church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you have any bridesmaids or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Only my hubby's sister. And my brother - Fred.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Can you remember if you had wedding presents from people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, I had quite a lot - yes. Different friends in the village that knew us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You didn't have a honeymoon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. I didn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I think you said you settled in a cottage on the outskirts of }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 Brails}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 ?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You went from there to a rent free house in a farm in the village?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Then you moved to Hook Norton in 1913?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And then in 1914 you went to Coventry?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 How long were you in Coventry?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Not long - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Less than a year?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I think it was less than a year.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 So when you came back did you live with your parents at first?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And then you found a cottage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Were you in that same cottage until the end of the war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No, I moved into another cottage. It was - they were both owned by Earl of Camperdown.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 How soon did you move into the next cottage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I think it was soon after I feel for my second - second son.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 About 1917?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Which of those house do you have the clearest recollection of your life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
Well, the first house that I had when we went back from Coventry that was a one bedroom and one place downstairs and just a small larder. That was all we had. The next house had a bigger living room and a bi
gger larder and a little kitchen at the back and two bedrooms.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Quite an improvement really?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. That was a - extra sixpence a week rent - one and six a week that was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When you married how old was your husband?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Oh - he was two years older than I - yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When you married him was he an agricultural labourer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
He'd been working at the brickyard. Yes. And he used to come over to me - see me twice a week. And he'd very often come before we'd finished our tea at night. And moth
er said to me, she said, I can't understand Bert. She said, how he gets off from work to get over here at this time of day. She said, a fellow like that, she says, is no good to you. She tried to put me off but really I worshipped the ground he walked on.
 I really did worship him and I thought the world of him.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Nothing'd stop me from marrying him although my parents were against it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was it just the fact he got off early do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, it wasn't - sad to say he hadn't been to work. No, he hadn't. No, he hadn't been at work - at this brickyard.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 But he said he was there did he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 He used to make out he'd been at work and I thought he'd been at work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Afterwards he worked in ironstone didn't he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did he do any casual jobs or part time jobs at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. Never.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 At some stage of his life did he go into farm work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, he was, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 That was later on was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 He was - he was in farm work after we left Galleyhill he was - went down in }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 Brails}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
 to live. He worked for the farmer to have the house rent free. Then we moved from there to Hook Norton and he worked at the ironstone works there for a little while then we went to Coventry. And he was a carter at the coal depot at Coventry. He took
 the coal out to the factories with a horse and cart. Then he was called up in the Derby scheme. He volunteered for service and been rejected three times before. But anyway they took him in the Derby scheme and - that was when I came home. Then after the 
war as he got demobbed we took a place at Garford. And that was agricultural and that seemed to be the turning point of my career. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You didn't have so much hardship after that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did he stay on in agricultural work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Always.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
When you did the bit of work - selling minerals and picking the blackberries and all that, did he have any views about your working because in those days some people used to disapprove of people working?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 He was glad I did go out and help him, yes. I used to go in the field with him and help him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did your husband like his own work or did he dislike it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 He liked farm work. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 But not the brickyards?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Your first son was born in 1912?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was he born at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. I went home to have him. Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you know what to expect in childbirth?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, I didn't. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 How did you get on and how did you find it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Very hard - I had a very hard - bad time - confinement first. I was really glad I was home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was your mother there to help you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes. She decided she'd like me to go home to have the babe and so my hubby came as well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 He came and stayed at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Used to go from our place to the - to }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 Brails}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551  to work.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 How long did you stay there with your mother then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Fortnight - quite a fortnight. 'Cos they didn't let you get up 'til the ninth day at that time of day. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you have any medical help at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Not a nurse or a doctor?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No. No. Mother used to wash and dress the babe and look after me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did she deliver the baby?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No we had a woman - what they called a midwife to deliver the wife. Looked her up beforehand.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Had she had any training?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Not special training - but they used to - they used to be what you might say the village midwife - they'd go anywhere.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 They'd have a lot of experience?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did anybody else help in the house at that time except your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 How did you feed that first baby?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Breast fed it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you enjoy feeding it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you have any difficulties with it at all and its feeding?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I used to have a wonderful lot of milk - yes. I had no trouble, you know, always seemed to have plenty milk for - all my children.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 If the baby was asleep and you thought it was time for a feed did you wake it up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No. Let it sleep - yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 If it cried before the normal time what did you do then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Give it the breast - very soon quiet.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you keep to a set pattern of hours for feeding or did you just feed it when it seemed to want feeding?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I didn't keep a set hours - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 How many times a day do you think it would work out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Oh about four. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Can you remember when you first gave it solid food?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
Milk - bread and milk - and biscuit. They used to make a - a very, very large tea biscuit - it was about half inch thick and about four inches across I should think and you used to soak them in a drop of
 water - put some sugar in and feed the babe from that. That was when you were weaning it from the breast.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 How old was it then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Oh, good twelve months - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you wean it suddenly or gradually?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Gradually - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Over what sort of period of time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Oh about a month,
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 So when you first stopped a feed and started on }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 solid}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551  food it was about twelve months old was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did it seem to mind being weaned?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, I don't think they noticed it because you'd start 
by giving it a - milk and biscuit do a - cut out one feed in the day - give it milk and biscuit. And then gradually wean it off the breast.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you think there was any harm in leaving a baby to cry?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Well, I never left my babies to cry long becau
se I was always afraid that they - rupture. That was the old fashioned ideas that the baby might rupture itself if it cried too long.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 How old was he when you first started punishing him for things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Well as soon as I knew pretty that it should have an idea that - that it was doing something wrong I'd give it a smack.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What sort of age?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Oh, eighteen months or two years. Yes. I think children at that time of day really did know if they was naughty.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 If when you were breast feeding the baby that it didn't seem hungry what did you do then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Just leave it - put it to bed - yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 The next one was called Cyril wasn't he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you feed Cyril in the same way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Any differences in how you fed him and weaned him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
I didn't feed Cyril so long. My mother was taken ill and we was - we was living at Garford and I had to go over to look after mother. I was breast feeding Cyril and he was about two months old. I walked from Hook Norton station home, that
 was five mile, pushed the push chair and my milk all went. From the walk I think it was. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 And I lost my milk and couldn't feed Cyril any longer so I put him on Glaxo - he was a Glaxo Baby.}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 That was in a bottle?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes. The old fashioned bottle
s that was a - flat shaped bottle with a long rubber tube - screwed - a screw in the top and a rubber tube with a glass end in the bottle and that come up to like a dummy to feed it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was it all straight away that your milk went?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. It went in less than a day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And didn't come back?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 How did Cyril take to the bottle?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Not very well at first. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was waking him for feeds and all that the same as with the older one - you didn't wake him for feeds at certain times?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, no. No, I used to give it him when I thought he, you know, hungry.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 His first solid food - was that the same?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, about the same.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And about the same time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, I think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When your babies were under a year old did your husband do anything to help with them at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 He'd have 'em - perhaps nurse 'em a bit at night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You mean if they woke in the night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did he ever give the bottle to Cyril?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What about things like bathing and changing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, he'd never do anything of that. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Would you expect him to or did you consider it was your job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Cyril - oh, he'd expect that was my work. But Cyril when he was born - I was afraid he was going to be blind baby. He had a discharge fr
om his eyes and I called in the doctor and - thinking it was a cold - and the doctor said it was something to do with the - when I was carrying him and he said, I'm afraid, he said, said, you've got a blind baby here. That was the biggest shock I've ever 
had in my life. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 
And he said there's only one thing you can do, he said, I'll get in touch with the nurse and you get some boras sic crystals - dissolve a teaspoonful of boras sic crystals in half a pint of water and dilute that he said and bathe your baby's
 eyes every two hours night and day, he said, and well see what we can do in a week. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
And my neighbour - I had a very good neighbour - she used to look after the baby in the daytime so that I could go to bed and she'd look after the baby in the daytime and 
I'd look after him at night. I'd sit up at night you see and do his eyes at night. And in about a fortnight doctor said he thought really - the bathing was working, you know, working out all right. Anyway - that babe was about - I should think he was abou
t
 twelve to eighteen months old - I've got him on my arm one day at the door and the bakers came down with a horse and trap and you know how a child'd go if he saw anything he - he jumped on my arm and oh I did feel happy. I thought you must - he must have
 seen that. He must have seen it, he hadn't got the knowledge to jump for the sound of }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 anything}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
. That was - that was the biggest shock I had to be told I had a blind baby and that was the biggest - happiest day I think of my life when I knew that he could see.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did your husband ever take them out with you when they were small?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Well he'd go out together with the pram - and push the pram.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Where would you go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Oh along the - along the lanes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did he ever take them out without you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, not very often - I don't remember. No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I wanted to ask you how you managed the housekeeping - I know you had a struggle those first years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 How much of your husbands earnings did he give to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I had it all - yes. A
nd it was seven and six - if it was seven and six I were lucky and if it were ten shillings - if he put a full week in well I was - I was in clover as you might say.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you and he discuss how the money should be spent?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 He used to trust me to pay my way and do the housekeeping. I used to buy his cigarettes. They were a penny for five.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 In that last house you were telling me about which was a bit bigger and you paid sixpence more - how many rooms were there all together?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 There was two bedrooms and a - a living room and a kitchen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And you were there about how many years before the end of the war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I was there from 19 - 1916 to 1919.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you have any relatives or lodgers living with you at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Not living with me - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Later you had your mother didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, after we moved - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You didn't pay anyone to help in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 How was your washing done?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I always used to do it myself - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You told me how your mother taught you to make a shirt for your husband?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you make anything else besides shirts?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, me underclothes and ....
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And for the children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you make a lot of things for them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you mend the clothes too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Always.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you ever buy any clothes in that time up until the end of the war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I used to buy some - suits - clothes for the children now and again when I could afford it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you buy anything for yourself and your husband?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Not much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Would you say that most of the clothes were bought or most were made?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I used to make what I could.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you ever buy secondhand clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Not very often.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Can you remember an occasion when you did buy secondhand clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. Unless it was at - at the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 flower show}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551  - they used to have a secondhand stall there. Sometimes I'd pick up a bargain.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Were they good quality secondhand clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, they were very good.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I think you said you always mended the shoes for the children and yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Even in those early days of your marriage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Oh, I should think it was 1920 odd when I started.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Before that what did you do about the mending?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Used to send them to the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 shoe mender}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you buy new shoes for yourself and the children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, but that wasn't very often. They seemed to wear much better that time of day than they do now - yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was there any special time of the year that you spent money on clothes and shoes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, only when we really needed them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You said you always did your own decorating?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you do that too in the first years of your marriage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you do anything else in the way of handwork and repairs and that sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I used to make - make wine and do me jam you see and - house decorating and shoe mending.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did your husband do anything of that kind?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 He used to help me - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did he do any washing up and cooking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What about things like dressing and undressing the children when they got older - telling them stories - that kind of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What time did your children go to bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 About seven - about seven.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Were they put to bed by you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Up to about what age did you put them to bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I used to see them to bed 'til time they left school - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did they share a bed or a bedroom?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 They shared one bedroom - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did they share a bed too or did they have separate beds?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No they had - shared the bed, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 There were two bedrooms weren't there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 So you and your husband had one?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 One and the - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What about bathing for your own children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 The washing bath.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Just the same as your own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
Yes, hot the water and tip it in and let then - if they could sit in it they were lucky. If they were small you see they could sit in the bath and have a bath. But as they grew older they used to stand in the bath.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What room did you do that in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 In the kitchen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 On a regular day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, in front of the fire usually on the Friday or Saturday night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What about the clean clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 They had - they had their clothes - they used to have their clothes - clean cl
othes then every end of week. Sometimes they'd have a clean shirt on in the week - midweek - if they - wanted it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Where did you have your meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 We had our meals in the living room - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was the kitchen very small there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Very small.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Would it have been big enough to eat in if you'd wanted to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
We might have got a very small table in there. There was a big open fireplace where you hung your pots and pans and a big baking oven over the top of the fire-place where you could cook or bake twenty or thirty loaves if you wanted.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you do that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
My neighbour used - we used to have the oven going every Sunday morning and my neighbour would find the wood one Sunday morning and I'd find it the other and we'd both cook ou
r meal in the one oven. We'd make enough pastry and cakes and puddings and that to last us pretty well the week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was she a good neighbour to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, ever such a good neighbour.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did she have young children as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You had your breakfast in the living room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you all have it together in the morning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Usually, yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What did you have for breakfast?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Bread and butter - bread and lard. Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was your main meal of the day midday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
No, was when - when my hubby worked in the - on the farm it was always a night meal. Usually he'd take his food if he was away on the farm - midday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And you'd have the main meal at night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What about the children - how did they manage for a main meal?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 They had the main meal the same time as we did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 They sat up for it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What time would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 About six o'clock. Half past five to six. And they'd have their wash and be put to bed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you have something with the children at midday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What sort of thing would you have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Well, if we were lucky we used to have a bit of bread and meat and ...
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Sometimes I suppose there was no meat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. Very often there were no meat.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What did you have then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Have a bit of dripping or something like that. Or I'd make a pan cake perhaps.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was it when Cyril was about one or two that you used to get the faggot and put it a pudding?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. And when I was first married I used to have to do that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did your mother help you at all at that time when you were very hard up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes. I used to walk from Browes to }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 Wychford}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551  to - to get something. I always come back with a piece of bacon, piece of cheese and lard - home cured lard, bag of }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 flour}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
 perhaps. I never went back home empty handed. I remember once my hubby hadn't done any work fortnight - it really was slack - it wasn't as he wouldn't work then - it was because the work was slack and it was wintertime and I hadn't ha
d any food from the Friday night 'til the - the Sunday excepting just a few boiled potatoes. Friday night I went out the back of the house and got some wood and I went down the granny - my hubby's grandmother and begged a match from her to light a fire - 
I
 boiled those few potatoes - I had no bread - and we had those few boiled potatoes on Friday night and I didn't have anything more 'til Sunday dinner time. I got up Sunday morning - I'd got the babe at the breast at the same time - and I got up at the Sun
day morning and I walked from Browes to }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 Wychford}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
. It was snowing hard all the way. My hubby didn't come with me - he trailed on behind.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Why?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I don't know, he didn't like to come I don't think in the first place and yet he-he knew very well that -
 I had to. And I remember I had to go just in front of the kitchen window and mother was dishing up the dinner - I well remember her words - she said, here comes our Florrie - she's got nothing to eat again. It was quite true. I sat and I enjoyed her - a 
n
ice cooked meal. After I had my meal I was took ill, I had to lay abed three days after that. That was exhaustion you see for - from the Friday night to the Sunday having that hot meal straight away. I'd have been better if I'd have had just something lig
ht and then gradually worked onto that hot meal. But mother didn't know at the time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Which baby was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Jessie. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you manage to go on feeding him?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When was it that you had to get the parish relief?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 At that time - yes, yes. When I went back home that - yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You went to see the vicar?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did they ask you a lot of questions when you went to see them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No. And we went to see the lady of the village and - I explained to her what 
had happened and - she asked me what the babe - what I fed the babe and I said well the doctor had ordered biscuits and whisky and a pint of milk a day extra to breast feed him and - so she went to the farmer and ordered the pint of milk for me and the ba
be and a two pound bag of biscuits and - she sent the groom up with a pint and a quarter bottle of whisky. And I think it was that really that saved my babe's life. That's Jessie - the one that's living with me now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was he very ailing then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 He wasn't very - healthy. His head hadn't closed and he was - well, little bit backward for a long time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Who was the lady of the village then that you went to see?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 A lady Gurney her name was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was her husband the Squire then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Don't she had a husband.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was she sort of an important person in the village?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes. The important person in that village.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And she was in charge of relief?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes. You could always depend on help if you went to her.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 How did she treat you in her manner?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Very nice. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you talk to your mother about how hard times were - did you and she discuss that sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, mother always knew when I was, you know, in a fix.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 She was a real good mother wasn't she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes
, and given me my rent - yes, and my brother. I went, the time that I've said that I went over that I was ill that two days, I even took a bag of coal tied at the back of the pram so that I should have some fire.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 She gave that to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. And my brother will - he gave me my rent for two weeks.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When you moved to Garford you'd been in the previous cottage during the birth of your second child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Can you remember about how long you were there - you moved I think you said when you were expecting him?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 About how old was he when you left there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Two years we were there - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And then you moved to Garford?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And I think it was when you were at Garford that you had to make that journey to see your mother when she wasn't well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 So Cyril was quite young then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 At that place before you went to Garford that was in }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 Wychford}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you have any relatives or lodgers living with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, not lodgers. I had a girl friend that slept with me while my hubby was in the forces.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 She just came in during the night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Just came at night and left in the morning. She lived in the village.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You didn't have any financial arrangement about that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you have any lodgers or relatives at any of your houses before the end of the war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
We had my husband's brother come to live with use after his mother died in 1920 when we were at Garford. We didn't have anybody before - anybody.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When your children were little did they have any jobs to do to help in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
Yes, I used to get them to get the bit of morning wood, clean their own shoes at night ready for school in the morning if they went to school. Saw that they cleaned their teeth and had a good wash at night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did they do anything else to help you on a Saturday for example?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Used to do the errands.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you give them pocket money for that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I used to buy them sweets I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 In the house where Cyril was born you mentioned that you used to make wine?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What kind of wine did you make?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Elderberry, sloe wine and - }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 potato}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551  wine.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And you made jam too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And pickles?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And beer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. Only ginger beer. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you bottle fruit or vegetables?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you make any home remedies or medicines for your children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, I generally depended on mother for that - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did she give you the same ones as she'd done for you when you were a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did your husband make any of those things I mentioned at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was he the sort of man who liked to do a bit of cooking or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No. No, he wasn't - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 At your last place in }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 Wychford}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551  did you grow fruit and vegetables at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
We had a garden. I kept two rabbits that the children - that the children, you know, as pets. We had a quite a nice garden and grew quite a lot of vegetables.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did it have fruit trees too or soft fruits?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Had one plum tree.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What about berry fruits?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 We had some currant trees I think - blackcurrant trees.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you buy vegetables and fruit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Never?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you keep any other livestock besides the rabbits?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 At that time how many times a week do you think you ate meat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Might be three.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What kind of meat would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Well a bit of butchers meat perhaps a shillings worth for the Sunday and Monday. If my hubby was in - when he was in the forces and I 
might have a bit of bacon in the week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 But that wasn't from your own pig - you didn't have a pig?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, no.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When you were first married how much meat did you have at that time? That was a harder time wasn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes. We were lucky if we had the trimmings from the bacon. We used to walk to }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 Shipton}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551  Saturday afternoons and for two shillings you could get enough bacon trimmings to last you pretty well a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What exactly were the trimmings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 They - as they cut the rashers the odd pieces - the misplaced pieces of rashers and that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And sometimes you would have nothing else but that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No. Only faggot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You had to give up having your meat pudding on a Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 How long did that bad time last?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Oh from - 'til the beginning of the war.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you remember having any tinned fruit yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Never.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Nothing tinned?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I don't remember tinned fruit in the - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And you don't remember having tinned meat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. I don't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you ever get anything poached?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you ever have to go short so that your husband and children could have more?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I've gone short many a time for my children to have extra. I always thought my hubby - if he was at work he needed sub
stantial as I could give him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 So you'd go short so he could have it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I'd go short myself - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you allow your children to talk during meals when they were little?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Not ordinary conversation I didn't. They spoke if I asked them anything - they'd answer me but that was all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Could they choose what they wanted to eat from what you'd cooked?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 If you cooked certain vegetables did you insist they had a bit of everything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Not if they didn't like it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 If they took something and they left it on the plate what would you say to that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 They'd have to have it in next meal. Yes. I didn't waste.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Can you remember an occasion when that happened?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Sometimes Jessie would leave his vegetable or - anythi
ng like that. And I used to put it in the larder and say, you'll have that for your next meal.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What did he say to that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 He didn't say anything - he took it fro granted, he knew I meant it and he knew the position and that was it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Could he ask for the cruet if he wanted it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 If it was within in his reach he'd take it but if not he'd ask me to pass or someone to pass it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Could he ask for a second helping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Always had it if there was any left.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you teach him to hold his knife and fork a certain way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Were you particular about the way he sat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
Mrs Davis said that she did not allow her children to bring toys or a book to the table, that all members of the family left the table at a mealtime
 after grace had been said. That if member of the family were present for a meal they all sat at the table, that everybody had their regular places at table. She also said that she served up the meal into dishes on the table as she had been brought up to 
d
o, and that when the children were off the breast they were fed from a high chair and she fed them at about the same time as she fed herself. She said that if they were as she put it - not up to the mark - she might sit them on her lap and give them a bit
 of food at the table. While they were at the state of weaning they would be fed before she had her own meal and gave her meal to her husband.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I asked if she thought that when she was - when her children were young that there was a right way and a wro
ng way of bringing up children and she said - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Your husband wasn't brought up as strict as you were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 So you would say that your ideas about bringing up children were a bit different?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Can you think of any particular thing where you used to differ at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
Well, he used to - sometimes he'd grumble if I wouldn't let them out to play rather later that what I usually did. Say if it was nearly seven o'clock and I wanted them in for bed he wouldn't agree with that. 
If it was summertime he'd say oh let them stop out a little bit longer. But I always liked to keep to the time and the ruling.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You think he had been allowed to stop out later himself as a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Oh yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When you said there was a right and a wrong way of bringing up children - what did you feel the right way was?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Well, discipline was chief thing. Always brought them up to respect other people and to try and help other people.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 If you were worried about the children when they were little was there anyone you used to talk to about it or weren't you ever worried?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Sometimes I was worried but if I could get home I always used to go home to mother. Always got advice from mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 How often do you think you saw her in those days when the children were very little
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When we lived in the village I saw her every day. Yes. And we moved to Browes we - I saw her once a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was that a regular sort of day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you go to her or did she come to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I always went to mother. She couldn't get about to come to see me - late years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you ever see your mother-in-law?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 She came to the wedding and I saw her once or twice after. Oh, and she came for a weeks holiday really to attend to the home and duties 
the time I was going to my second - the third babe, Arthur. And I didn't have him at the scheduled date and her went back home - left me, I had to depend on the neighbour that I hadn't asked anything about.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You mean you didn't know the neighbour?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I hadn't asked her about attending me. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you ever discuss the children with your mother-in-law?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Never. No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you think you and she had the same ideas about that kind of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I don't think so. I never had much to really say to her.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Would you say you had the same ideas about children as your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes. Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Can you tell me some of the things you felt you }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 ought}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551  to do for your children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you think it important to show children affection?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Oh, I think it matters a wonderful lot. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What about safety - did that concern you much when you were a young mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Safety - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you think a lot about their food?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I used to give them the best I could afford.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you want them to grow up so that they could tell their worries to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, I should have - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 How did you want them to behave towards you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Well, I should - I wanted them to show the affection that I should expect to them a
nd I think they all did. I think they all think the world of me, all along all my lifetime I can't remember for what anyone of them would have helped me if I'd said to 'em I want help. Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When grown ups came to the house or you were with grown ups did you let your children join in during a conversation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you mean visitors? I've got to think - I don't believe I ever had anybody come to stop. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Perhaps if you went to your mothers and you and she were talking would you allow them to join in the conversation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
When you said you wanted to bring them up to consider other people and always help them can you think of anything else you brought them up to consider important in life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Always tell the truth and to be honest.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Same as you had been brought up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 If they said that another child hit them what would you say to them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You must hit them back. I wouldn't interfere.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Were there any children that you discouraged them from playing with when they were little?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, I don't remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 If your children did something you disapproved of what would happen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I would give - I would give 'em a smack if it wasn't - if it was trivial. But if they really done anything that I thought was beyond
 it I used to give them the belt - or the - or the - inner tube of the bicycle. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 How often do you think that happened?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Oh, very seldom. Yes. Yes, they knew word - I kept my word. I didn't say oh, if you do so-and-son I'll give you a good hid
ing. If I said I'd hit them I'd hit them straight away.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 How often do you think you had to hit them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Oh, probably once a week. It might be.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did your husband punish them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. Never remember him punishing either of the children.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Can you remember any particular occasion when you had to punish them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 There was the time when your mother was upset because of the bad word.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you punish him then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did your mother?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 She sat him on the - on the stove - she didn't half give him a grumble at and she shook him - I don't say...
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Which one was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 That was Jessie. He'd been out to play with some other children and he came in and something suit him - he said oh, damn it. She s
aid, I've never heard that word mentioned in my home before, she said. She blamed me for it. I said, well mother, I haven't - I haven't let him hear a word like that - I wouldn't say it myself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 But you can't keep them away from everybody can you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You don't remember a time when you did punish them - anything that they got up to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
No, I - not really - not to give them a - extraordinary good hiding. I put them into bed first. That was the biggest punishment that I could give my children.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You'd give them the belt?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Make them stop in bed a whole day. Yes. Take their clothes away and just let them have their meals - no book or anything to look at.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Would you say that your children received the ideas they had about behaviour from both of you or more from you or more from your husband?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 More from me. I don't think my hubby would have troubled much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Didn't he care too much about that sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When they got a little bit older did he ever take them out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, no. Not much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did he not have a lot to do with them when they were small children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Well, he was at work you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 They worked such long hours didn't they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When you went out hoeing in the field - did you do that while they were very little or when they were older?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When Jessie was about - six months old I went out in the summertime hoeing in the field.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What did you do about feeding him then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Gave him the breast.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did he come with you then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. I took him in the field in the pram. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you keep him in sight then while you hoed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you ever leave the children when you went into the field work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. Always took them with me - wherever I went I took them with me.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you think it was necessary that they be with you all the time or did you think it was sometimes good for them to be with other people?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When they were small I always kept them with me. There was no such thing as stay 
- having - someone stay with your children while you went out. Nobody ever seemed to go out at night - if they'd got children they stay home with them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 So you never left your children with somebody else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. Only mother - when I went shopping.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You'd go over to her with them would you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When your children had a birthday would it be different from any other day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, perhaps they'd have - one or two of their schoolfriends in and I'd get a little }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 tea party}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551  - make a jelly or something like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did they have any presents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 The children that came to tea sometimes'd bring a little present for them. And it was generally in the way of wearing }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 apparel}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551  that I got for - for them, some-thing that'd be useful. I never remem
ber Jessie having a toy. Only the doll that I had given me when I was a girl.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You don't remember buying him a toy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. Never.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Can you remember anything you did with your husband and children on Christmas Day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Well, it was very much - more or less like an ordinary day. Never went out anywhere.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You didn't go to chapel on Christmas Day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you see your mother on Christmas Day at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Sometimes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you have anything special to eat or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Used to always have a plum pudding as they called it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you have any musical instruments?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 We had a small - very small harp - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Who played that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I did. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Where did you learn to play the harp?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Oh, I just picked up it - picked it up by ear.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And you used to sing too didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did your husband sing or play?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 He run a dance band late in life - yes, yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 At that time did he do any playing or singing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 He was a member of the Browes Mission Band and he played the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 euphonium}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did he have an instrument of his own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you remember you and him ever singing together or making music together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you play games with the children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Which ones were those?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Well, all of them as they got older.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Which games?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Oh, ball - cricket and hide and seek.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you play table games like snakes and ladders?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. That was the only game ever learnt.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And ludo?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did your husband join in the games?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did he play any games with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, not with the children - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you have any books in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Not very often. I remember - I remember buying one or two. That was when a Missionary came
 to the village and he sold books for the children and I might buy 'em a tuppenny or thruppenny book then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What about newspapers - did you get a newspaper?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And magazines?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you belong to a library?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was there one you could have joined?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you remember reading aloud to the children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Sometimes I'd read before they went to sleep at night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you ever read to your husband?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did he read to you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did he ever read to the children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you remember taking the older two children when they were little out visiting? You took them to your mother?
