\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you have a bicycle at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, I had a bicycle after I was married.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you go for long rides at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. I didn't get out much. In fact I swapped my bicycle for the first pram. I didn't have the bike long.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Anything at all in entertainments - concerts or music-halls or gatherings.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I used to go to chapel anniversary. That was once a year and they used to have a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid14375446\charrsid1600551 tea party}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551  at chapel and mother used to be caretaker of the chapel. I used to help her sometimes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And they had music then of course didn't they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 They used to have a service and then get the children and that to sing and recite.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Can you think of anything at all you did outside the home - or was your life your home and family at that time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I don't remember doing anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Being on the parish council and all that came later in life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes. That's since I've been at Wootton. Yes. I didn't enter into any activities 'til we was at }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid14375446\charrsid1600551 Ascot-under-Whychwood}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 . And I became a member of the W.I. there and that was the first time that I 
seemed to take any interest outside the home. That was about 1924 or '25. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 While you were - while the children were little you had this help from your mother
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Was it your brother Fred who helped you with the rent on one occasion?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Anybody else help you at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Well, my brother will would help me sometimes. He'd give me a shilling or two shillings.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did your neighbour ever help you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I had one }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14375446\charrsid1600551 neighbour}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551  at }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 Wychford}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551  that helped me when I had Cyril that he was nearly blind. She came to help - yes.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Were you ever sick at that time when the children were little and had to stop in bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, I don't remember, ever having to -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 That was fortunate?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Besides your mother and sister there wasn't any other relative you used to go and see?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you ever have friends into the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you ever remember neighbours or friends just calling in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes. They would just come in for a chat, yes, you know - that's about all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you give them anything to eat or drink?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No. Couldn't afford it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 People had just enough for themselves didn't they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When you got together with neighbours would it just be a chat or would you have music or games?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, no. No music. Just a chat or talk. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 At that time your house was rented wasn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 And also at }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 Wychford}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When you were at }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9571655\charrsid1600551 Wychford}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551  who was your landlord there - was it the Earl of Camperdown?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you ever see him or meet him personally?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 What did you think of him as a landlord?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Well, the agent used to collect the rent. He used to come to the school once a year in September and collect the 
rent. So we never saw anything of the Earl of Camperdown.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 How do you think he looked after the property - would you say he was a good, bad or average landlord?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Oh, he was average landlord.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When you had this very bad time when you were at Brailles was it because your husband was ill or was it because he was out of work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Out of work - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14375446\charrsid1600551 Was he was laid off or was it because he didn't go?}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 He just couldn't get work - there was no work about. There was always plenty of empty h
ouses at that time of day when I was young. Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 You moved house a lot really didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Would you say that your mother and father had the same attitude to people in different social classes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I think they'd treat everyone as, you know, the same.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you think your mother saw herself as belonging to a certain social class?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 I think she just termed herself as a working class person.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Why do you think she thought of herself in that way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Probably she was brought up in that way to - help other people and that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you think it could have been because of her parents being working class or because of her husband being a working man?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 It might have been. Yes. My mother's parents was a - her father was a wheelwright and carpenter. Under - undertaker as well - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Do you think at that time when you were a girl and a young woman there was a great division between trained }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14375446\charrsid1600551 craftsmen}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551  and other workers who didn't have a trade?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Not socially I don't think there was - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 But in what way then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Well, if they went out and about more - they had more money I think to go to different events and that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 When you used to go out doing your work in the fields did you think the farmers who were em
ploying you and the working people had the same interests or different.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Well, they'd - I think they'd always think theirselves just a little bit higher class than we were. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did they show this to you in the way they behaved?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 No, no, no.
 It may have been the way that I was brought up to always think of the farmers and that in a different position to what I was. Was always yes Sir and no Sir - everything like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13458850 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Did you bring your own children up to be like that?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16061682 FD  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16607957\charrsid1600551 Yes. Yes. And I always brought my children up the same as I - never to break a promise if they could help it. My main motto in life.

\par }}